n%20struck%20with%20what%20%26quot%3Blooked%20like%20a%20knife%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEmergency%20responders%20were%20seen%20carrying%20Lee%20into%20an%20ambulance.%20He%20was%20later%20taken%20to%20hospital%20on%20a%20helicopter%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Yonhap%20news%20agency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20agency%20said%20he%20was%20bleeding%20but%20conscious%20as%20he%20was%20transported%20to%20the%20Pusan%20National%20University%20Hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20an%20act%20of%20terror%20against%20Lee%20and%20a%20serious%20threat%20to%20democracy%20that%20should%20never%20occur%20under%20any%20circumstances%2C%26quot%3B%20Kwon%20Chil-seung%2C%20an%20MP%20from%20Lee's%20Democratic%20Party%2C%20told%20reporters%20outside%20the%20hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20to%20Lee's%20condition%2C%20we%20are%20waiting%20for%20the%20medical%20staff's%20assessment%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added%2C%20demanding%20a%20%26quot%3Bthorough%26quot%3B%20police%20investigation%20into%20the%20attack.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20in%20Busan%20said%20Lee%20suffered%20a%20%26quot%3Bone-centimetre%20laceration%20on%20his%20neck%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20he%20%26quot%3Bremains%20conscious%20and%20bleeding%20is%20minor%26quot%3B%2C%20according%20to%20South%20Korean%20news%20outlet%20Chosun%20Ilbo.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETV%20footage%20showed%20police%20officials%20wrestling%20the%20attacker%20to%20the%20ground.%20He%20was%20seen%20wearing%20a%20hat%20with%20Lee's%20name%20on%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYonhap%20said%20the%20assailant%20has%20been%20arrested.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EPresidential%20contender%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELee%20lost%20in%202022%20to%20conservative%20Yoon%20Suk%20Yeol%20in%20the%20tightest%20presidential%20race%20in%20South%20Korea's%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYoon%20expressed%20%26quot%3Bdeep%20concern%20over%20the%20safety%20of%20Lee%20Jae-myung%20upon%20hearing%20of%20the%20attack%26quot%3B%2C%20his%20spokeswo