%20under%20fire%20from%20members%20of%20his%20own%20Conservative%20Party%20for%20allowing%20migration%20to%20soar%20-%20via%20both%20legal%20and%20irregular%20routes%20into%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Conservatives%20made%20control%20over%20the%20UK%20border%20a%20central%20argument%20for%20the%202016%20decision%20to%20leave%20the%20European%20Union.%20One%20of%20the%20Tories'%20key%20election%20pledges%20in%202019%20was%20to%20reduce%20net%20migration.%20Instead%2C%20it%20soared%20to%20a%20record%20745%2C000%20last%20year%2C%20although%20a%20vast%20majority%20came%20through%20legal%20routes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20sees%20clearing%20the%20backlog%20of%20asylum%20cases%20as%20well%20as%20sending%20those%20who%20arrive%20to%20Rwanda%20as%20essential%20to%20reducing%20the%20UK's%20appeal%20to%20migrants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20illegal%20entries%20across%20Europe%20are%20going%20up%2C%20the%20number%20of%20people%20coming%20into%20the%20UK%20illegally%20is%20going%20down%2C%26quot%3B%20Home%20Secretary%20James%20Cleverly%20said.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20significant%20achievement%2C%20but%20the%20job%20is%20far%20from%20over.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704166620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2F817ag8s_rishi-sunak-bloomberg_625x300_05_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuk-making-progress-in-stopping-small-boat-migration-says-rishi-sunak-4784527%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prime%20Minister%20Rishi%20Sunak%20said%20his%20government%20has%20made%20progress%20on%20limiting%20migration%20to%20the%20UK%2C%20pointing%20to%20reductions%20in%20the%20number%20of%20people%20arriving%20without%20permission%20and%20in%20the%20backlog%20of%20asylum%20cases.%22%2C%22