0at%20the%20port%2C%20where%20a%20seven-storey%20building%20collapsed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlmost%2045%2C000%20households%20were%20without%20power%20in%20the%20region%20which%20saw%20temperatures%20touch%20freezing%20overnight%2C%20the%20local%20energy%20provider%20said.%20Many%20cities%20were%20without%20running%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20Geological%20Survey%20(USGS)%20said%20the%20quake%20had%20a%20magnitude%20of%207.5.%20Japan's%20meteorological%20agency%20measured%20it%20at%207.6%2C%20and%20said%20it%20was%20one%20of%20more%20than%20150%20to%20shake%20the%20region%20through%20Tuesday%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20strong%20jolts%20were%20felt%20early%20Tuesday%2C%20including%20one%20measuring%205.6%20percent%20that%20prompted%20national%20broadcaster%20NHK%20to%20switch%20to%20a%20special%20programme.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPlease%20take%20deep%20breaths%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20presenter%20said%2C%20reminding%20viewers%20to%20check%20for%20fires%20in%20their%20kitchens.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ETsunami%20warning%20lifted%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%20waves%20at%20least%201.2%20metres%20(four%20feet)%20high%20hit%20Wajima%20on%20Monday%2C%20and%20a%20series%20of%20smaller%20tsunamis%20were%20reported%20elsewhere.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20warnings%20of%20much%20larger%20waves%20proved%20unfounded%20and%20on%20Tuesday%20Japan%20lifted%20all%20tsunami%20warnings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EImages%20on%20social%20media%20showed%20cars%20and%20houses%20in%20Ishikawa%20shaking%20violently%20and%20terrified%20people%20cowering%20in%20shops%20and%20train%20stations.%20Houses%20collapsed%20and%20huge%20cracks%20appeared%20in%20roads.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20team%20of%20firefighters%20crawled%20under%20a%20collapsed%2C%20large%20commercial%20building%20in%20Wajima%2C%20television%20footage%20showed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHang%20in%20there!%20Hang%20in%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20shouted%20as%20they%20battled%20through%20piles%20of%20wooden%20beams%20with%20an%20electric%20saw.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20were%20shaking%20that%20I%20have%20never%20experienced%20before%2C%20a%20local%20elderly%20man%20told%20NHK.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInside%20my%20house%2C%20it%20was%20so%20terrible...%20I%20am%20still%20alive.%20Maybe%20I%20have%20to%20%C2%A0be%20content%20with%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fire%20in%20Wajima%20engulfed%20a%20row%20of%20houses%2C%20video%20footage%20showed%2C%20with%20people%20being%20evacuated%20in%20the%20dark%2C%20some%20with%20blankets%20and%20others%20carrying%20babies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20duty%20officer%20at%20Wajima%20Fire%20Department%20said%20they%20still%20were%20being%20overwhelmed%20Tuesday%20by%20rescue%20requests%20and%20reports%20of%20damages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20total%20of%2062%2C000%20people%20had%20been%20ordered%20to%20evacuate%2C%20according%20to%20the%20fire%20and%20disaster%20management%20agency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbout%201%2C000%20people%20were%20staying%20at%20a%20military%20base%2C%20the%20defence%20ministry%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EBullet%20trains%20suspended%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDefense%20Minister%20Minoru%20Kihara%20said%201%2C000%20military%20personnel%20were%20preparing%20to%20go%20to%20the%20region%2C%20while%208%2C500%20others%20were%20on%20standby.%20Around%2020%20military%20aircraft%20were%20dispatched%20to%20survey%20the%20damage.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMonday's%20quake%20shook%20apartments%20in%20the%20capital%20Tokyo%20some%20300%20kilometres%20away%2C%20where%20a%20public%20New%20Year%20greeting%20event%20that%20was%20to%20be%20attended%20by%20Emperor%20Naruhito%20and%20his%20family%20members%20was%20cancelled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20major%20highways%20were%20closed%20around%20the%20epicentre%2C%20Japan's%20road%20operator%20said%2C%20and%20bullet%20train%20services%20from%20Tokyo%20were%20also%20suspended.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJapan%20experiences%20hundreds%20of%20earthquakes%20every%20year%20and%20the%20vast%20majority%20cause%20no%20damage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20country%20has%20strict%20regulations%20intended%20to%20ensure%20buildings%20can%20withstand%20strong%20quakes%20and%20routinely%20holds%20emergency%20drills.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20country%20is%20haunted%20by%20the%20memory%20of%20a%20massive%209.0-magnitude%20undersea%20quake%20off%20northeastern%20Japan%20in%20March%202011%2C%20which%20triggered%20a%20tsunami%20that%20left%20around%2018%2C500%20people%20dead%20or%20missing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%202011%20tsunami%20also%20sent%20three%20reactors%20into%20meltdown%20at%20the%20Fukushima%20nuclear%20plant%2C%20causing%20Japan's%20worst%20post-war%20disaster%20and%20the%20most%20serious%20nuclear%20accident%20since%20Chernobyl.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJapan's%20nuclear%20authority%20said%20there%20were%20no%20abnormalities%20reported%20at%20the%20Shika%20atomic%20power%20plant%20in%20Ishikawa%20or%20at%20other%20plants%20after%20Monday's%20quake.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Washington%2C%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20was%20briefed%20on%20Monday's%20quake%20and%20offered%20Japan%20%26quot%3Bany%20necessary%20assistance%26quot%3B%20to%20cope%20with%20the%20aftermath.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrench%20President%20Emmanuel%20Macron%20expressed%20%26quot%3Bsolidarity%26quot%3B%20while%20Italian%20Prime%20Minister%20Giorgia%20Meloni%20offered%20condolences%20and%20assistance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704164580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F5b2n5olg_fumio-kishida_120x90_02_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fjapan-earthquake-casualties-numerous-damage-extensive-pm-fumio-kishida-4784081%22%2C%22summa