aid%20the%20quake%20had%20a%20magnitude%20of%207.5.%20Japan's%20meteorological%20agency%20measured%20it%20at%207.6%2C%20and%20said%20it%20was%20one%20of%20more%20than%20150%20to%20shake%20the%20region%20through%20Tuesday%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20strong%20jolts%20were%20felt%20early%20Tuesday%2C%20including%20one%20measuring%205.6%20percent%20that%20prompted%20national%20broadcaster%20NHK%20to%20switch%20to%20a%20special%20programme.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPlease%20take%20deep%20breaths%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20presenter%20said%2C%20reminding%20viewers%20to%20check%20for%20fires%20in%20their%20kitchens.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ETsunami%20warning%20lifted%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%20waves%20at%20least%201.2%20metres%20(four%20feet)%20high%20hit%20Wajima%20on%20Monday%2C%20and%20a%20series%20of%20smaller%20tsunamis%20were%20reported%20elsewhere.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20warnings%20of%20much%20larger%20waves%20proved%20unfounded%20and%20on%20Tuesday%20Japan%20lifted%20all%20tsunami%20warnings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EImages%20on%20social%20media%20showed%20cars%20and%20houses%20in%20Ishikawa%20shaking%20violently%20and%20terrified%20people%20cowering%20in%20shops%20and%20train%20stations.%20Houses%20collapsed%20and%20huge%20cracks%20appeared%20in%20roads.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20team%20of%20firefighters%20crawled%20under%20a%20collapsed%2C%20large%20commercial%20building%20in%20Wajima%2C%20television%20footage%20showed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHang%20in%20there!%20Hang%20in%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20shouted%20as%20they%20battled%20through%20piles%20of%20wooden%20beams%20with%20an%20electric%20saw.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20were%20shaking%20that%20I%20have%20never%20experienced%20before%2C%20a%20local%20elderly%20man%20told%20NHK.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInside%20my%20house%2C%20it%20was%20so%20terrible...%20I%20am%20still%20alive.%20Maybe%20I%20have%20to%20%C2%A0be%20content%20with%