n%2C%20tension%2C%20will%20cease%20to%20exist%20and%20everyone%20will%20be%20happy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E'Ram%20Rajya'%20is%20a%20term%20used%20to%20refer%20to%20an%20ideal%20governance%20where%20everyone%20is%20happy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20greetings%20and%20blessings%20to%20all%20countrymen%20on%20New%20Year.%20Ram%20Lalla%20will%20be%20offered%20'Chhapan%20Bhog'%2C%20and%20'prasad'%20will%20be%20offered%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20shortly%20before%20heading%20for%20the%20Ramjanmabhoomi%20temple%20site%20to%20perform%20the%20'aarti'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20customs%2C%20'Bhog%20aarti'%20is%20performed%20at%20noon.%20A%20'Chappan%20Bhog'%20is%20offered%20to%20Ram%20Lalla%20on%20special%20occasions%20such%20as%20Holi%2C%20Ramnavmi%2C%20Basant%20Panchami%2C%20New%20Year%2C%20and%20Independence%20and%20Republic%20Day%2C%20his%20side%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%2C%20the%20new%20year%20will%20be%20very%20good%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20Ram%20temple's%20chief%20priest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20'Chhappan%20Bhog'%20offered%20to%20Ram%20Lalla%20on%20Monday%20had%20come%20in%20a%20specially%20made%20box%20bearing%20a%20design%20that%20depicted%20Lord%20Ram%20and%20the%20upcoming%20temple%2C%20from%20a%20very%20old%20shop%20in%20Lucknow%2C%20his%20aide%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20it%20has%20been%20coming%20from%20the%20very%20same%20place%20for%20the%20last%20few%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20New%20Year%20is%20very%20significant%2C%20and%20it%20is%20significant%20because%20in%20this%20month%20on%20January%2022%2C%20Ram%20Lalla%20will%20be%20seated%20in%20the%20sanctum%20sanctorum%20(of%20the%20under-construction%20temple)...and%20this%20will%20be%20very%20beneficial%20for%20the%20people%20of%20the%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20Acharya%20Das%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%20in%20Ayodhya%2C%20organisers%20began%20distributing%20worshipped%20'akshat'%20--%20rice%20grains%20mixed%20with%20turmeric%20and%20ghee%20--%20on%20New%20Year's%20Day%20and%20this%20will%20continue%20up%20to%20January%2015%2C%20a%20week%20before%20the%20consecration%20ceremony%20at%20the%20Ram%20temple.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAyodhya%20rang%20in%20the%20New%20Year%20on%20December%2031%20night%2C%20amid%20chants%20of%20'Jai%20Shri%20Ram'%20as%20many%20residents%20and%20others%20had%20gathered%20at%20the%20iconic%20Lata%20Mangeshkar%20Chowk%20near%20Naya%20Ghat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20large%20number%20of%20people%20took%20holy%20dip%20in%20the%20Saryu%20river%20on%20the%20New%20Year%20while%20others%20visited%20the%20Ramjanmabhoomi%20temple%20to%20have%20a%20'darshan'%20of%20Ram%20Lalla%2C%20as%20well%20as%20Hanumangarhi%20temple%20to%20seek%20blessings%20of%20Lord%20Hanuman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20the%20further%20construction%20of%20the%20Ram%20temple%2C%20this%20year%2C%20Das%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20work%20is%20to%20be%20done%20in%202024.%20One%20is%20that%20Ram%20Lalla%20will%20be%20seated%20in%20the%20sanctum%20sanctorum.%20And%2C%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20also%20will%20take%20place%20in%20this%20year%2C%202024%2C%20and%20all%20these%20will%20be%20'shubh'%20(propitious)%20and%20good.%26quot%3B%20The%20consecration%20ceremony%20will%20take%20place%20few%20months%20ahead%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20visited%20the%20temple%20town%20on%20December%2030%20during%20which%20he%20held%20a%20roadshow%2C%20inaugurated%20the%20redeveloped%20Ayodhya%20railway%20station%20and%20the%20newly-bult%20airport%2C%20and%20laid%20foundation%20stone%20for%20a%20slew%20of%20other%20projects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20August%205%2C%202020%2C%20he%20had%20performed%20the%20'bhoomipujan'%20ceremony%20in%20Ayodhya%20for%20the%20upcoming%20temple.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESettling%20a%20fractious%20issue%20that%20goes%20back%20more%20than%20a%20century%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%20a%20historic%20verdict%20in%202019%20backed%20the%