jungle-13040698%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fvenezuelan-family-living-american-dream-after-epic-journey-across-11-countries-and-notorious-jungle-13040698%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fvenezuelan-family-living-american-dream-after-epic-journey-across-11-countries-and-notorious-jungle-13040698%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Around%20675%2C000%20cans%20of%20hypoallergenic%20infant%20formula%20have%20been%20recalled%20over%20concerns%20of%20bacteria%20contamination%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20baby%20bottle%20on%20a%20countertop.%20A%20person%20with%20a%20baby%20is%20in%20the%20background.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6593148e1c5c7b8c9a0d2500%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EVera%20Vita%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EReckitt%2FMead%20Johnson%20Nutrition%20recently%20recalled%20some%20batches%20of%C2%A0a%20hypoallergenic%20infant%20formula.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThere%20was%20%26quot%3Ba%20possibility%20of%20contamination%20with%20Cronobacter%20sakazakii%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20recall%20announcement%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EReckitt%2FMead%20Johnson%20Nutrition%20agreed%20to%20start%20a%20recall%20involving%20roughly%C2%A0675%2C000%20cans.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EReckitt%2FMead%20Johnson%20Nutrition%20is%20recalling%20around%20675%2C000%20cans%20of%20hypoallergenic%20infant%20formula%20over%20a%20possible%20bacteria%20contamination.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fda.gov%2Fsafety%2Frecalls-market-withdrawals-safety-alerts%2Freckittmead-johnson-nutrition-voluntarily-recalls-select-batches-nutramigen-hypoallergenic-infant%23recall-announcement%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%20in%20a%20press%20release%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20it%20was%20voluntarily%20recalling%20batches%20of%20its%20Nutramigen%20Powder%2C%20which%20is%20made%20to%20manage%20cow%20milk%20allergies%2C%20%26quot%3Bdue%20to%20a%20possibility%20of%20contamination%20with%20Cronobacter%20sakazakii%20in%20product%20sampled%20outside%20the%20U.S.%26quot%3B%20The%20recall%20of%20the%20formula%20is%20tied%20to%2012.6%20and%2019.8%20oz%20cans%20of%20the%20product.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20there%20weren't%20reports%20of%20either%20%26quot%3Billnesses%20or%20adverse%20events%26quot%3B%20tied%20to%20the%20product%2C%20which%20was%20distributed%20throughout%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20according%20to%20the%20announcement%2C%20the%20bacteria%20can%20cause%20meningitis%20and%20%26quot%3Bsevere%2C%20life-threatening%20infections%2C%26quot%3B%20including%20sepsis.%20While%20the%20release%20noted%20the%20potential%20contamination%2C%20it%20also%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Bother%20testing%20of%20the%20batches%20in%20question%20tested%20negative%20for%20Cronobacter%20and%20other%20bacteria.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20infant%20formula%20firms%20are%20required%20to%20test%20a%20representative%20sample%20of%20their%20product%20for%20both%20Cronobacter%20and%20Salmonella%20species%2C%20this%20important%20verification%20step%20does%20not%20guarantee%20the%20product%20is%20free%20of%20Cronobacter%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20update%20from%20Sunday%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fda.gov%2Ffood%2Fcfsan-constituent-updates%2Freckittmead-johnson-nutrition-voluntarily-recalls-certain-nutramigen-hypoallergenic-powdered-infant%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EFood%20and%20Drug%20Administration%20site%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20said.%20%26quot%3BCronobacter%20contamination%20can%20occur%20at%20very%20low-levels%20and%20is%20not%20evenly%20distributed%20throughout%20the%20product%2C%20making%20it%20difficult%20to%20detect.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERecalled%20cans%20feature%20the%20following%20batch%20codes%3A%20ZL3FHG%2C%20ZL3FMH%2C%20ZL3FPE%2C%20ZL3FQD%2C%20ZL3FRW%2C%20and%20ZL3FXJ.%20The%20cans%20have%20a%20UPC%20Code%20of%20300871239418%20or%20300871239456%2C%20and%20use%20by%20date%20of%20January%201%2C%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BConsumers%20who%20purchased%20Nutramigen%20should%20check%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20can%20to%20identify%20whether%20the%20batch%20number%20is%20affected%2C%26quot%3B%20Reckitt%2FMead%20Johnson%20Nutrition%20said.%20%26quot%3BProduct%20with%20the%20batch%20codes%20listed%20above%20should%20be%20disposed%20of%2C%20or%20contact%20us%20for%20a%20total%20refund.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20recent%20update%20on%20the%20Food%20and%20Drug%20Administration%20site%20said%20after%20a%20recommended%20recall%2C%20%26quot%3BReckitt%2FMead%20Johnson%20Nutrition%20agreed%20to%20initiate%20a%20voluntary%20recall%20of%20675%2C030%20cans%20of%20Nutramigen%20powdered%20infant%20formula%20distributed%20to%20the%20United%20States.%26quot%3B%20That%20agreement%20was%20on%20December%2029.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20to%20Business%20Insider%2C%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20Reckitt%2FMead%20Johnson%20said%20the%20formula%20in%20the%20recall%20was%20manufactured%20in%20June%202023%20and%20primarily%20distributed%20between%20June%20and%20August%20%26quot%3Bafter%20testing%20negative%20for%20bacteria%20prior%20to%20distribution%20per%20Reckitt%2FMead%20Johnson's%20standard%20protocol%20of%C2%A0rigorous%20and%20industry-leading%20quality%20tests%20and%20checks.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20spokesperson%20said%20that%20after%20it%20was%20alerted%20in%20December%20to%20a%20%26quot%3Bpotential%20cross%20contamination%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bthe%20FDA%20and%20Reckitt%2FMead%20Johnson%20both%20tested%20samples%20from%20the%20batch%20in%20question%20and%20all%20testing%20has%20been%20negative%20for%20Cronobacter.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20Reckitt%2FMead%20Johnson%20understands%20the%20incredible%20responsibility%20we%20have%20in%20providing%20what%20is%20often%20the%20sole%20nutrition%20for%20infants%2C%20and%20there%20can%20be%20no%20short%20cuts%20for%20this%20vulnerable%20population%20%E2%80%93%20therefore%2C%20we%20chose%20to%20recall%20select%20batches%20of%20Nutramigen%20out%20of%20an%20abundance%20of%20caution%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20said.%20%26quot%3BParents%20should%20be%20reassured%20that%20they%20can%20continue%20to%20feed%20their%20infants%20with%20Reckitt%2FMead%20Johnson%20Nutrition%20products%2C%20including%20other%20Nutramigen%20powder%20formula%20batches%2C%20with%20confidence.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBack%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbaby-formula-recall-impacts-some-similac-alimentum-elecare-products-2022-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E2022%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20US%20had%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbiden-baby-formula-shortage-fda-european-abbott-nutrition-2022-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Elarge%20infant%20formula%20shortage%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20steps%20were%20taken%20to%20try%20to%20mitigate%20the%20shortage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20FDA%20said%20it%20doesn't%20expect%20the%20recent%20recall%20to%20have%20a%20%26quot%3Bmajor%20impact%26quot%3B%20on%20the%20supply%20and%20availability%20of%20powdered%20infant%20formulas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20agency%20remains%20committed%20to%20helping%20ensure%20an%20adequate%20supply%20of%20infant%20formula%20and%20giving%20consumers%20the%20utmost%20confidence%20that%20infant%20formula%20available%20in%20the%20U.S.%20is%20safe%20and%20nutritious%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20FDA%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freckitt-mead-johnson-nutrition-recall-infant-formula-powder-cans-2024-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704151132000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F659314