%20new%20aircraft%20carrier%20is%20returning%20to%20the%20US%20after%20being%20sent%20into%20waters%20near%20Israel.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20USS%20Gerald%20R.%20Ford%20Carrier%20Strike%20Group%20was%20sent%20to%20stop%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20war%20from%20expanding.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20CSG's%20deployment%20was%20repeatedly%20extended.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20Navy%20is%20finally%20bringing%20the%20USS%20Gerald%20R.%20Ford%20Carrier%20Strike%20Group%20home%20after%20it%20was%20abruptly%20tasked%20to%20the%20eastern%20Mediterranean%20in%20response%20to%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20war%20and%20kept%20at%20sea%20longer%20than%20planned.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Ford%20carrier%20strike%20group%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-navy-newest-supercarrier-deployment-unexpected-turn-israel-crisis-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ewas%20sent%20to%20the%20eastern%20Mediterranean%20in%20October%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20during%20its%20first%20full%20deployment%20in%20an%20effort%20to%20%26quot%3Bcontribute%20to%20our%20regional%20deterrence%20and%20defense%20posture%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Navy%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20sudden%20outbreak%20of%20violence%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20which%20started%20with%20the%2010%2F7%20Hamas%20terror%20attacks%2C%20continued%20with%20Israel's%20war%20against%20Gaza%2C%20and%20has%20since%20spread%2C%20led%20to%20repeated%20extensions%20of%20the%20Ford%20CSG's%20deployment.%20The%20strike%20group%20has%20been%20at%20sea%20for%20over%20240%20days%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.usni.org%2F2024%2F01%2F01%2Fcarrier-uss-gerald-r-ford-heading-home-after-8-months-2-extensions%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eper%3C%2Fa%3E%20USNI%20News.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20coming%20days%20though%2C%20the%20new%20first-in-class%20carrier%20and%20its%20escort%20ships%20will%20return%20to%20its%20homeport%20in%20Norfolk%2C%20Virginia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20fighting%20broke%20out%20between%20Israel%20and%20Hamas%20in%20October%2C%20the%20new%20supercarrier%20made%20its%20way%20toward%20the%20unfolding%20crisis%20accompanied%20by%20the%20Ticonderoga-class%20guided-missile%20cruiser%20USS%20Normandy%20and%20the%20Arleigh%20Burke-class%20guided-missile%20destroyers%20USS%20Thomas%20Hudner%2C%20USS%20Ramage%2C%20USS%20Carney%2C%20and%20USS%20Roosevelt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20later%20sent%20the%20Dwight%20D.%20Eisenhower%20Carrier%20Strike%20Group%20into%20the%20Mediterranean%20and%20the%20Middle%20East%20for%20added%20deterrence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20warships%20with%20the%20Ford%20and%20Eisenhower%20strike%20groups%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ehave%20been%20operating%20in%20the%20Red%20Sea%2C%20where%20they%20have%20responded%20to%20Houthi%20missile%20and%20drone%20attacks%20on%20commercial%20shipping.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20mission%20of%20the%20naval%20forces%20present%20in%20the%20area%20has%20been%20to%20show%20support%20for%20Israel%20after%20the%20attacks%20by%20Hamas%20and%20also%20deter%20additional%20attacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20has%20also%20provided%20other%20military%20support.%20%26quot%3BThe%20United%20States%20government%20will%20be%20rapidly%20providing%20the%20Israel%20Defense%20Forces%20with%20additional%20equipment%20and%20resources%2C%20including%20munitions%2C%26quot%3B%20US%20defense%20secretary%2C%20Lloyd%20Austin%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-moves-carrier-group-capable-of-firing-guided-missiles-to-israel-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Esaid%20in%20October%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Additional%20air%20assets%20were%20also%20deployed%20to%20the%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20the%20Ford%20carrier%20strike%20group%20is%20redeploying%20to%20its%20homeport%20to%20prepare%20for%20future%20tasking%2C%20the%20Navy%20will%20continue%20to%20maintain%20a%20presence%20in%20the%20Mediterranean%20and%20the%20Middle%20East.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20presence%20will%20include%20elements%20of%20the%20Eisenhower%20CSG%20and%20additional%20warships%2C%20such%20as%20the%20amphibious%20assault%20ship%20USS%20Bataan%20and%20dock%20landing%20ship%20USS%20Carter%20Hall%2C%20which%20are%20joining%20the%20transport%20dock%20ship%20USS%20Mesa%20Verde%20to%20form%20an%20%3Cspan%3EAmphibious%20Ready%20Group.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Department%20of%20Defense%20continually%20evaluates%20force%20posture%20globally%20and%20will%20retain%20extensive%20capability%20both%20in%20the%20Mediterranean%20and%20across%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Navy%20release%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-navy-aircraft-carrier-returning-home-after-extended-deployment-2024-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704149480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65257a6555f52b01b35b229a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-navy-aircraft-carrier-returning-home-after-extended-deployment-2024-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Navy's%20newest%20aircraft%20carrier%20is%20being%20redeployed%20back%20to%20the%20US%20after%20being%20sent%20to%20the%20eastern%20Mediterranean%20in%20October.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jpandy%40insider.com%20(Jordan%20Pandy)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A34%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-navy-aircraft-carrier-returning-home-after-extended-deployment-2024-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pak%20human%20rights%20body%20says%20an%20upcoming%20election%20is%20unlikely%20to%20be%20free%20and%20fair%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704149289000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106461341%2Cimgsize-123888.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fpakista