124010101068_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Risks%20Of%20%26quot%3BDonkey%20Flights%26quot%3B%20As%20Illegal%20Migration%20Rises%20In%20Punjab%2C%20Haryana%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIllegal%20immigration%20by%20young%20Indians%20to%20countries%20such%20as%20the%20US%2C%20the%20UK%2C%20and%20Canada%20has%20come%20under%20spotlight%20as%20a%20plane%20carrying%20suspected%20victims%20of%20human%20trafficking%20was%20rerouted%20to%20India.%20The%20flight%2C%20which%20made%20headlines%20last%20week%2C%20was%20on%20its%20way%20to%20Nicaragua%20after%20being%20detained%20in%20France.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDonkey%20Flight%26quot%3B%20has%20become%20the%20catchall%20term%20for%20such%20illegal%20movements%20--%20a%20corruption%20of%20the%20Punjabi%20work%20%26quot%3Bdunki%26quot%3B%20meaning%20to%20hop%20from%20one%20place%20to%20another.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvery%20year%20more%20than%2020%2C000%20young%20men%20and%20women%20from%20Punjab%20attempt%20irregular%20migration%2C%20the%20United%20Nations%20Office%20on%20Drugs%20and%20Crime%20hjhad%20said%20in%20a%20report%20back%20in%202009.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20intercepted%20flight%20indicated%2C%20the%20number%20has%20only%20grown.%20While%20no%20consolidated%20data%20exists%20given%20the%20secrecy%20exercised%2C%20there%20are%20other%20indicators.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%202012%2C%20the%20Punjab%20Police%20have%20issued%20over%2010%20lakh%20Police%20Clearance%20Certificates%20(PCC)%20--%20a%20spike%20that%20raises%20aspirations%20even%20among%20those%20of%20the%20young%20generation%20who%20have%20no%20means%20to%20move%20abroad.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Special%20Investigation%20Team%20has%20handled%20about%20645%20such%20cases%2C%20resulting%20in%20518%20arrests%2C%20Anil%20Vij%2C%20the%20Home%20Minister%20Haryana%20has%20said%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20process%20is%20not%20easy.%20Apart%20from%20the%20high%20financial%20cost%2C%20there%20is%20every%20risk%20of%20being%20thrown%20into%20jail%20at%20any%20stage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20agent%20had%20promised%20to%20send%20me%20to%20Italy%20for%2012%20lakhs%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Rahul%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Haryana's%20Kurukshetra%2C%20recalling%20his%20bid%20to%20migrate%20a%20few%20months%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20April%208%2C%20they%20sent%20me%20first%20to%20Dubai%20and%20then%20to%20Egypt%20and%20was%20told%20that%20I%20will%20be%20sent%20to%20Libya%20from%20where%20I%20will%20have%20a%20direct%20flight%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20he%20managed%20to%20reach%20Libya%2C%20he%20soon%20found%20the%20cost%20was%20too%20great%20--%20landing%20in%20jail%20shortly%20after.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20day%20he%20suffered%20a%20heart%20attack%20in%20jail.%20Thought%20to%20be%20dead%2C%20he%20was%20thrown%20on%20the%20sand%20outside.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20people%20in%20the%20jail%20protested%20seeing%20me%20like%20this%20and%20tried%20to%20break%20the%20jail.%20Then%20I%20was%20taken%20to%20the%20hospital.%20As%20soon%20as%20I%20came%20to%20my%20senses%2C%20I%20was%20taken%20by%20the%20people%20of%20the%20Embassy%20and%20after%20making%20a%20white%20passport%2C%20I%20was%20brought%20to%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20others%20are%20not%20lucky%20enough%20to%20make%20it%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShiv%20Kumar%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Kaithal%2C%20sent%20his%20son%20to%20Portugal%20mortgaging%20his%20ancestral%20land.%20For%20the%20last%20seven%20months%2C%20he%20has%20been%20running%20from%20pillar%20to%20post%20to%20get%20his%20son%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20a%20police%20case%20has%20been%20lodged%20against%20the%20agent%20who%20sent%20his%20son%20abroad%2C%20there%20is%20no%20clue%20to%20the%20young%20man's%20whereabouts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTill%20date%2C%20we%20do%20not%20know%20where%20our%20son%20is.%20We%20last%20spoke%20to%20him%20on%20June%208.%20Two%20agents%20got%20bail%20and%20are%20now%20on%20the%20run...%20I%20have%20appealed%20to%20many%20places...%20lodged%20a%20complaint%20on%20the%20government's%20Madad%20App%20but%20no%20help%20came.%20We%20came%20to%20know%20that%20a%20boat%20on%20way%20from%20Libya%20to%20Italy%20sank%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added%2C%20breaking%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20others%2C%20like%20Malkeet%20from%20Kaithal%20district%2C%20the%20journey%20proved%20fatal.%3Cbr%3E%5CnHis%20family%20got%20to%20know%20of%20his%20death%20from%20a%20video%20that%20had%20gone%20viral.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENDTV%20approached%20many%20travel%20agents%20seeking%20details.%20Only%20one%20person%20agreed%20to%20speak%20on%20condition%20of%20anonymity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20two%20kind%20of%20illegal%20routes%20through%20which%20we%20send%20people%20abroad.%20One%20is%20through%20the%20forest%20route%20which%20is%20less%20expensive%20--%20around%2030-40%20lakh...%20these%20days%20Turkey%20is%20the%20transit%20point...%20From%20Turkey%20a%20visa%20for%20Costa%20Rica%20is%20obtained...then%20to%20Panama%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20payment%20has%20to%20be%20made%20in%20tranches%20at%20every%20phase%20--%20Rs%2010%20lakh%20has%20to%20be%20paid%20in%20Turkey%2C%20another%2010%20lakh%20in%20Costa%20Rica%20and%20final%20payments%20have%20to%20be%20made%20in%20two%20tranches%20at%20the%20Mexico%20border.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20second%20category%2C%20the%20travel%20is%20by%20air%2C%20which%20costs%20around%20Rs%2040%20to%2050%20lakh%20and%20the%20people%20are%20sent%20by%20air%20through%20any%20European%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20so%2C%20dozens%20of%20Indians%20are%20taking%20to%20social%20media%20to%20document%20their%20journey%2C%20offering%20tips%2C%20route%20suggestions%20and%20risk%20assessments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20flight%20returned%20from%20Bangalore%2C%20both%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana%20have%20cracked%20down%20on%20fake%20agents.%20Punjab%20has%20formed%20a%20Special%20Investigation%20Team%20to%20probe%20the%20issue.%C2%A0%20Haryana%20said%20it%20already%20has%20one%2C%20which%20has%20been%20going%20after%20the%20fraudulent%20agents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20state%20government%20will%20bring%20a%20bill%20in%20the%20winter%20session%20of%20the%20state%20assembly%20to%20regulate%20immigration%20agents%20and%20agencies%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Anil%20Vij.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704131700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fjn0gafag_donkey-flight_625x300_01_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frisks-of-donkey-flights-as-illegal-migration-rises-in-punjab-haryana-4782758%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Illegal%20immigration%20by%20young%20Indians%20to%20countries%20such%20as%20the%20US%2C%20the%20UK%2C%20and%20Canada%20has%20come%20under%20spotlight%20as%20a%20plane%20carrying%20suspected%20victims%20of%20human%20trafficking%20was%20rerouted%20to%20India.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frisks-of-donkey-flights-as-illegal-migration-rises-in-punjab-haryana-4782758%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frisks-of-donkey-flights-as-illegal-migration-rises-in-punjab-haryana-4782758%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frisks-of-donkey-flights-as-illegal-migration-rises-in-punjab-haryana-4782758%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Working%20Towards%20Closing%20Down%201%2C000%20Private%20Madrassas%3A%20Assam%20Chief%20Minister%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Assam%20government%20is%20trying%20to%20negotiate%20with%20private%20madrassas%20for%20their%20closure%20and%20conversion%20to%20general%20schools%2C%20Chief%20Minister%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%20said%20on%20New%20Year's%20day.%20This%20comes%20after%20his%20government%20has%20already%20shut%20down%20all%20government-run%20madrassas%20in%20the%20state%20and%20converted%20them%20to%20general%20schools.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPrivate%20madrassas%20are%20protected%20by%20the%20constitutions%20of%20India%20as%20it%20is%20written%20that%20the%20government%20cannot%20touch%20minority-run%20educational%20institutes.%20They%20don't%20even%20fall%20under%20the%20RTE%20Act.%20But%20having%20said%20that%2C%20the%20Assam%20police%20and%20education%20department%20are%20working%20together%20so%20we%20can%20reduce%20at%20least%201000%20private%20madrassas.%20From%20three%20thousand%2C%20it%20will%20come%20down%20to%20two%20thousand%20and%20we%20are%20negotiating%20this%20with%20the%20private%20madrassa%20bodies%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20five%20distinct%20communities%20who%20are%20known%20as%20Assamese%20Muslim%20communities%2C%20we%20have%20approved%20the%20census%20and%20we%20are%20verifying%20the%20villages%20where%20the%20Assamese%20Muslim%20communities%20live%2C%20also%20wards%20in%20municipal%20areas%20where%20Assamese%20Muslims%20live%20are%20being%20earmarked%20and%20by%20the%20end%20of%202024%2C%20we%20will%20complete%20this%20census%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Sarma%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Assam%20Chief%20Minister%20also%20added%20that%20his%20government%20will%20complete%20a%20fresh%20census%20of%20Assamese%20Muslims%20by%20the%20end%20of%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESignificantly%2C%20Mr%20Sarma%20said%20that%20at%20least%20two%20more%20districts%20of%20Assam%20will%20see%20a%20rollback%20of%20AFSPA%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Assam%20government%20has%20now%20recommended%20a%20total%20withdrawal%20but%20the%20Government%20has%20advised%20us%20that%20we%20need%20to%20be%20a%20little%20cautious%20so%20AFSPA%20is%20now%20restricted%20to%20four%20districts.%20I%20think%20in%20the%20next%20review%2C%20we%20will%20roll%20back%20AFSPA%20from%20two%20other%20districts%2C%20The%20Centre%20does%20not%20want%20to%20withdraw%20AFSPA%20from%20the%20triangle%20area%20of%20the%20borders%20between%20Assam%2C%20Nagaland%20and%20Arunachal.%20It's%20a%20matter%20of%20time%2C%20at%20some%20point%20in%20time%20AFSPA%20will%20totally%20be%20rolled%20back%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704131520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-08%2F1346v45g_himanta-biswa-sarma-pti_625x300_11_August_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fworking-towards-closing-down-1-000-private-madrassas-assam-chief-minister-4782727%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Assam%20government%20is%20trying%20to%20negotiate%20with%20private%20madrassas%20for%20their%20closure%20and%20conversion%20to%20general%20schools%2C%20Chief%20Minister%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%20said%20on%20New%20Year's%20day.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fworking-towards-closing-down-1-000-private-madrassas-assam-chief-minister-4782727%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fworking-towards-closing-down-1-000-private-madrassas-assam-chief-minister-4782727%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fworking-towards-closing-down-1-000-private-madrassas-assam-chief-minister-4782727%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bharti%20Airtel%20Services%20set%20to%20acquire%2097.1%25%20stake%20in%20Beetel%20Teletech%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704131350000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2021-09%2F01%2Ffull%2F1630436084-3893.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fbharti-airtel-services-set-to-acquire-97-1-stake-in-beetel-teletech-124010101018_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Pegging%20the%20cost%20of%20acquisitio