%20Says%20Congress%20as%20MGNREGA%20Wage%20Payment%20Through%20Aadhaar%20System%20Kickstarts%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F11%2F03131216%2FScreen-Shot-2021-11-03-at-1.07.58-PM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Congress%20has%20condemned%20the%20linking%20of%20the%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20National%20Rural%20Employment%20Guarantee%20Act%2FScheme%20(MGNREGA%2FS)%20to%20Aadhaar%20that%20takes%20off%20from%20Monday%20(January%201)%20and%20has%20called%20it%20a%20%E2%80%9Ccruel%20new%20year%20gift%E2%80%9D%20to%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20poor%20and%20marginalised.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20scheme%20guarantees%20100%20days%20of%20work%20to%20rural%20households.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20implementation%20of%20an%20Aadhaar-based%20payment%20system%20was%20made%20mandatory%20on%20January%2030%2C%202023%2C%20and%20after%20five%20extensions%20for%20state%20governments%20to%20calibrate%20their%20databases%2C%20it%20is%20set%20to%20kickstart%20from%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20system%20requires%20a%20worker%E2%80%99s%20bank%20account%20and%20job%20card%20to%20be%20linked%20with%20Aadhaar.%20The%20account%20must%20also%20be%20connected%20to%20the%20National%20Payments%20Corporation%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98mapper%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fnew-year-new-rule-for-mgnrega-workers%2Farticle67692863.ece%5C%22%3Edata%20by%20LibTech%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20consortium%20of%20academics%20and%20activists%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fnrega-job-card-deletions-aadhaar-mechanism-tech-solutions-ineffective%5C%22%3E7.6%20crore%20job%20cards%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20been%20deleted%20from%20the%20system%20over%20the%20last%2021%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20on%20Monday%2C%20Congress%20MP%20and%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20media%20and%20communication%20in-charge%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20said%20that%20the%20move%20was%20the%20%E2%80%9Cprime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20cruel%20new%20year%20gift%20to%20exclude%20crores%20of%20the%20poorest%20and%20marginalised%20Indians%20from%20earning%20a%20basic%20income.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20in%20total%2025.69%20crore%20MGNREGA%20workers%20of%20whom%2014.33%20crore%20are%20considered%20as%20active%20workers.%20As%20on%20December%2027%2C%2034.8%25%20of%20the%20total%20registered%20workers%20(8.9%20crore)%20and%2012.7%25%20of%20active%20workers%20(1.8%20crore)%20are%20still%20ineligible%20for%20ABPS.%20Despite%20many%20challenges%20highlighted%20by%20workers%2C%20practitioners%2C%20and%20researchers%2C%20in%20using%20ABPS%20for%20MGNREGA%20wage%20payments%2C%20the%20Modi%20government%20has%20continued%20with%20its%20destructive%20%E2%80%98experiments%20with%20technology%E2%80%99.%20This%20is%20the%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20cruel%20new%20year%20gift%20to%20exclude%20crores%20of%20the%20poorest%20and%20marginalised%20Indians%20from%20earning%20a%20basic%20income%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERamesh%20accused%20the%20Modi%20government%20of%20using%20technology%20as%20a%20weapon%20to%20exclude%20the%20people%20belonging%20to%20the%20marginalised%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20well-known%20disdain%20for%20MGNREGA%20has%20translated%20into%20a%20slew%20of%20experiments%20designed%20to%20use%20technology%20as%20a%20weapon%20to%20exclude%20%E2%80%93%20such%20as%20the%20digital%20attendance%20(NMMS)%2C%20ABPS%2C%20drone%20monitoring%2C%20and%20the%20proposed%20integration%20of%20facial%20recognition%20to%20NMMS.%20No%20due%20consultation%20or%20scientific%20piloting%20was%20done%20before%20unleashing%20these%20%E2%80%98experiments%E2%80%99%20on%20crores%20of%20Indians%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20reiterated%20its%20earlier%20demand%20that%20the%20Union%20government%20%E2%80%9Cshould%20stop%20weaponising%20technology%2C%20especially%20Aadhaar%2C%20to%20deny%20the%20most%20vulnerable%20Indians%20their%20social%20welfare%20benefits%2C%20release%20delayed%20wage%20payments%20and%20implement%20open%20muster%20rolls%20and%20social%20audits%20to%20improve%20transparency.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20its%20popularity%2C%20the%20job%20scheme%20has%20seen%20budget%20cuts%20in%20recent%20years.%20In%20the%202023%20budget%2C%20the%20MGNREGS%20was%20allocated%20Rs%2060%2C000%20crore.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fnikhil-dey-mgnrega-budget-cut-2023%5C%22%3EConcerns%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20been%20raised%20that%20the%20allocation%20to%20the%20MGNREGS%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Fnrega-budget-allocation-2023-24%5C%22%3Edeclined%20by%2033%25%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20compared%20to%20the%20revised%20estimates%20of%202022-23.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%20%3C%2Fem%3Ehas%20earlier%20reported%20that%20the%20centrally%20sponsored%20scheme%20has%20not%20had%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fcag-audit-mgnrega-10-years-serious-questions%5C%22%3Eperformance%20audit%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20Comptroller%20and%20Auditor%20General%20(CAG)%20since%202013.%20CAG%E2%80%99s%20performance%20audits%20examine%20the%20extent%20to%20which%20an%20activity%2C%20programme%2C%20or%20organisation%20operates%20economically%2C%20efficiently%2C%20and%20effectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704107333000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F11%2F03131216%2FScreen-Shot-2021-11-03-at-1.07.58-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcruel-new-year-gift-says-congress-as-mgnrega-wage-payment-through-aadhaar-system-kickstarts%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20implementation%20of%20an%20Aadhaar-based%20payment%20system%20was%20made%20mandatory%20on%20January%2030%2C%202023%2C%20and%20after%20five%20extensions%20for%20state%20governments%20to%20calibrate%20their%20databases%2C%20it%20is%20set%20to%20kickstart%20from%20January%201.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A13%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcruel-new-year-gift-says-congress-as-mgnrega-wage-payment-through-aadhaar-system-kickstarts%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%20About%20the%20Memory%20of%20Perpetrators%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F01162813%2FIMG_2641.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20May%202013%2C%20Argentinian%20journalist%20Jorge%20Kostinger%20sent%20the%20following%20letter%20to%20the%20Videla%20family%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20the%20Videla%20family%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%20is%20the%20body.%20Without%20filing%20a%20request%20for%20%3Cem%3Ehabeas%20corpus%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20you%20have%20the%20body.%20A%20few%20forms%20to%20fill%2C%20and%20it%20is%20yours%2C%20you%20can%20take%20away%20your%20relative%E2%80%99s%20mortal%20shell.%20You%20have%20a%20body.%20You%20will%20notice%20that%20it%20is%20delivered%20to%20you%20without%20any%20burns%20or%20bruises.%20We%20could%20at%20least%20have%20given%20it%20a%20richly%20deserved%20beating.%20We%2C%20however%2C%20prefer%20not%20to%20do%20the%20things%20that%20the%20body%20that%20you%20are%20going%20to%20bury%20did.%20We%20did%20not%20throw%20it%20out%20of%20a%20plane%2C%20we%20did%20not%20encourage%20it%20to%20%E2%80%9Csqueal%E2%80%9D%20using%20electric%20shocks.%20To%20squeal%2C%20for%20example%2C%20about%20where%20our%20bodies%2C%20those%20of%20our%20comrades%2C%20are.%20We%20did%20not%20rape%20it.%20We%20did%20not%20put%20its%20child%20on%20its%20chest%20while%20we%20cranked%20the%20generator.%20We%20did%20not%20shoot%20it%20in%20order%20to%20pretend%20that%20it%20died%20in%20a%20stand-off.%20We%20did%20not%20encase%20it%20in%20concrete.%20We%20did%20not%20bury%20it%20in%20an%20unmarked%20grave%20somewhere.%20We%20did%20not%20steal%20its%20grandchildren.%20Here%2C%20the%20body%20is%20yours.%20(cited%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tandfonline.com%2Fdoi%2Ffull%2F10.1080%2F14623528.2018.1459230%5C%22%3ES%C3%A9vane%C2%A0Garibian%3C%2Fa%3E)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20body%20belonged%20to%20General%20Jorge%20Rafael%20Videla%2C%20notorious%C2%A0%20Commander%20in%20Chief%20of%20the%20Argentinian%20army%20and%20%3Cem%3Ede%20facto%20%3C%2Fem%3Edictator%20between%201976%20and%201981%2C%20during%20whose%20reign%20of%20terror%20upwards%20of%2020%2C000%20persons%2C%20by%20one%20estimate%2C%20mostly%20politically%20active%20people%2C%20were%20%E2%80%98disappeared%E2%80%99.%20At%20least%2010%2C000%20of%20these%20%5Bpeople%5D%20have%20never%20been%20found%2C%20even%20as%20skeletal%20remains%2C%20and%20these%20are%20the%20subject%20of%20the%20famous%20Mothers%20of%20the%20Plaza%20campaign%20since%20the%201980s.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKostinger%E2%80%99s%20letter%20shows%20barely%20controlled%20anger.%20Referencing%20all%20the%20horrific%20modes%20of%20torture%20performed%20on%20thousands%20of%20Argentinian%20citizens%2C%20Kostinger%20tells%20the%20Videla%20family%20that%20the%20dictator%E2%80%99s%20body%20was%20never%20defiled%2C%20never%20desecrated%3A%20the%20body%20is%20intact%2C%20possesses%20its%20own%20integrity%20still%2C%20unlike%20the%20many%20victims%20of%20Jorge%20Rafael%20Videla.%20It%20is%20ready%20for%20memorialisation%20%E2%80%93%20an%20honour%20%3Cem%3Enot%3C%2Fem%3E%20available%20to%20his%20victims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20much%20has%20been%20said%20and%20written%20about%20the%20mourning%20and%20memorialisation%20for%20the%20victims%2C%20the%20question%20arises%2C%20how%20does%20one%20memorialise%20perpetrators%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20perpetrator%20here%20is%20not%20a%20serial%20killer%20or%20everyday%20offenders%20of%20civil%20or%20criminal%20law%2C%20but%2C%20in%20the%20words%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sup.org%2Fbooks%2Ftitle%2F%3Fid%3D34348%5C%22%3EAntonius%20C.G.M.%20Robben%20and%20Alexander%20Laban%20Hinton%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9Cactive%20participants%20in%20state%20institutions%20and%20repressive%20organisations%20or%20informal%20associations%20and%20networks%20who%20carry%20out%20genocide%2C%20mass%20killings%2C%20or%20violent%20acts%20for%20the%20presumed%20greater%20good%20of%20the%20state%2C%20a%20people%2C%20or%20an%20ideology.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F01132828%2Fimage-1681.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F01132828%2Fimage-1681.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F01132828%2Fimage-1681-300x150.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F01132828%2Fimage-1681-1024x511.png%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F01132828%2Fimage-1681-800x400.png%20800w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-691177%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22599%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EWhile%20much%20has%20been%20said%20and%20written%20about%20the%20mourning%20and%20memorialisation%20for%20the%20victims%2C%20the%20question%20arises%2C%20how%20does%20one%20memorialise%20perpetrators%3F%20Photo%3A%20Unsplash%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Fhow-to-indict-persecutors%5C%22%3EHow%20to%20Indict%20Perpetrators%20%E2%80%93%20Nuremberg%E2%80%99s%20History%20Lessons%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIn%20the%20absence%20of%20%3Cem%3ECorpus%20delicti%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Videla%E2%80%99s%20time%2C%20there%20were%20very%20few%20%3Cem%3Ecorpus%20delicti%3C%2Fem%3E%20(evidence%20of%20a%20crime%20committed%2C%20particularly%20in%20the%20form%20of%20a%20corpse).%20Both%20the%20living%20and%20the%20dead%20were%20%E2%80%98disappeared%E2%80%99.%20As%20stated%20in%20the%20official%20report%20on%20the%20Argentinian%20disappearances%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.desaparecidos.org%2Fnuncamas%2Fweb%2Fenglish%2Flibrary%2Fnevagain%2Fnevagain_001.htm%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ENunca%20M%C3%A1s%3A%20The%20Report%20of%20the%20Argentine%20National%20Commission%20on%20the%20Disappeared%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20(1986)%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%5BThe%5D%20absence%20giving%20hope%20to%20the%20relatives%20that%20the%20kidnap%20victim%20would%20be%20freed%20and%20return%3B%20then%20the%20concealment%20and%20destruction%20of%20documen%C2%ADtation%2C%20which%20undoubtedly%20existed%20in%20every%20case%2C%20prolonging%20the%20uncertainty%20about%20what%20had%20happened%3B%20and%20finally%2C%20the%20nameless%20bodies%2C%20without%20identity%2C%20driving%20people%20distraught%20at%20the%20impos%C2%ADsibility%20of%20knowing%20the%20specific%20fate%20of%20their%20loved%20one.%20It%20was%20a%20bottomless%20pit%20of%20horror.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20thousands%20killed%20in%20the%20S-21%20prison%20of%20the%20Khmer%20Rouge%20during%20the%20years%20of%20terror%20were%20indexed%20in%20the%20form%20of%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Fwhy-atrocity-archives-exist-and-why-we-need-them%5C%22%3Ephotographic%20archive%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20at%20least.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20context%20where%20families%20and%20communities%20mourn%20the%20very%20absence%20of%20bodies%20%E2%80%93%20and%20the%20absence%20is%2C%20oddly%2C%20evidence%20that%20something%20is%20rotten%20in%20the%20state%20%E2%80%93%20the%20debate%20around%20the%20rights%20of%20dictators%E2%80%99%20families%20or%20the%20state%20itself%20to%20commemorate%2C%20memorialise%2C%20and%20thereby%20%E2%80%98honour%E2%80%99%20the%20dictator%20becomes%20a%20thorny%20issue.%20Take%20for%20instance%2C%20the%20case%20of%20Talaat%20Pasha%2C%20often%20seen%20as%20the%20man%20behind%20the%20Armenian%20massacres.%20After%20his%20assassination%20in%201921%2C%20he%20was%20given%20a%20grand%20burial%20in%20Berlin.%20Later%2C%20Adolf%20Hitler%20transferred%20the%20remains%20to%20Istanbul%2C%20and%20it%20is%20now%20in%20a%20mausoleum%20built%20in%20the%20memory%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98heroes%20of%20the%20fatherland%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Nazis%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nationalww2museum.org%2Fwar%2Ftopics%2Fnuremberg-trials%5C%22%3Econvicted%20at%20Nuremberg%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20not%20subject%20to%20public%20executions%2C%20although%20the%20photographs%20of%20their%20dead%20bodies%20were%20released.%20Hitler%E2%80%99s%20body%2C%20at%20his%20own%20orders%2C%20was%20burnt%20immediately%20after%20his%20suicide%20in%20the%20Berlin%20bunker.%20The%20subject%20of%20where%20Spain%E2%80%99s%20Franco%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-46048514%5C%22%3Eshould%20be%20interred%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20in%20the%20tomb%20in%20the%20Valle%20de%20los%20Cai%CC%81dos%20or%20in%20the%20cemetery%20near%20his%20former%20residence%20in%20the%20palace%20of%20El%20Pardo%20%E2%80%93%20has%20been%20the%20subject%20of%20controversy.%20The%20same%20applies%20to%20the%20body%20of%20Pol%20Pot%20and%20the%20other%20leaders%20of%20the%20Cambodia%2FKhmer%20Rouge%20reign.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20many%20massacred%20or%20disappeared%20do%20not%20have%20a%20topography%20of%20remains%20%E2%80%93%20the%20body%2C%20a%20grave%2C%20a%20tombstone%2C%20an%20annual%20prayer%2Fritual%20%E2%80%93%20how%20does%20the%20national%20or%20community%20mourning%20of%20the%20principal%20human%20cause(s)%20of%20the%20massacre%20operate%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20many%20survivors%2C%20the%20tyrants%20by%20dying%2C%20escaped%20the%20processes%20of%20justice%20at%20the%20hands%20of%20the%20law.%20For%20example%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aljazeera.com%2Fnews%2F2006%2F8%2F10%2Fcambodias-long-wait-for-justice%5C%22%3EPol%20Pot%E2%80%99s%20trial%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20underway%20when%20he%20died%20and%20for%20many%20families%20of%20his%20victims%2C%20he%20had%20%E2%80%98got%20away%E2%80%99%20by%20dying.%20That%20is%2C%20the%20impunity%20with%20which%20they%20operated%20in%20massacring%20and%20maiming%20thousands%20when%20alive%2C%20extended%20to%20them%20even%20after%20their%20reign%20and%20to%20their%20deaths.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShould%20the%20corpses%20of%20the%20perpetrator%20be%20treated%20as%20%3Cem%3Ecorpus%20delicti%3C%2Fem%3E%3F%20Does%20this%20corpse%2C%20of%20the%20perpetrator%2C%20bring%20about%20closure%20for%20survivors%20of%20those%20s%2Fhe%20had%20executed%3F%20Or%20does%20the%20very%20presence%20of%20the%20perpetrator%E2%80%99s%20corpse%2C%20often%20interred%20grandly%2C%20mark%20the%20transformation%20of%20the%20villain%20into%20a%20hero%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F01140941%2FBundesarchiv_Bild_183-V04744_Berlin_Garten_der_zerst%25C3%25B6rte_Reichskanzlei-1.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221019%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F01140941%2FBundesarchiv_Bild_183-V04744_Berlin_Garten_der_zerst%25C3%25B6rte_Reichskanzlei-1.jpg%20800w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F01140941%2FBundesarchiv_Bild_183-V04744_Berlin_Garten_der_zerst%25C3%25B6rte_Reichskanzlei-1-300x189.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-691186%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22642%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EExterior%20of%20the%C2%A0%3Cspan%20title%3D%5C%22German-language%20text%5C%22%3EF%C3%BChrerbunker%3C%2Fspan%3E%20shortly%20before%20its%20destruction.%20Hitler%20and%20Braun%E2%80%99s%20remains%20were%20burnt%20in%20a%20shell%20crater%20outside%20the%20emergency%20exit%20at%20the%20left.%20Photo%3A%20Bundesarchiv%2C%20Bild%20183-V04744%2FCC-BY-SA%203.0%2FWikimedia%20Commons%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETrying%20memories%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20judicial%20process%20operates%20as%20not%20just%20an%20occasion%20for%20remembering%20the%20horrors%20%E2%80%93%20many%20victims%20break%20down%2C%20as%20occurred%20in%20the%20Cambodia%2FKhmer%20Rouge%20trials%20and%20even%20at%20the%20South%20African%20Truth%20and%20Reconciliation%20Commission%20hearings%20%E2%80%93%20but%20also%20as%20a%20means%20of%20bringing%20the%20perpetrators%20to%20public%20account.%20This%20involves%20questions%2C%20practices%2C%20and%20the%20ethics%20of%20memory-making.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20perp%20is%20put%20on%20trial%20%E2%80%93%20from%20Nuremberg%201945%20to%20Cambodia%202009%20%E2%80%93%20what%20is%20being%20made%20public%20is%20a%20memorialisation%20of%20their%20victims%2C%20but%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20the%20perpetrator.%20The%20testimony%20of%20witnesses%20%E2%80%93%20though%20this%20was%20not%20the%20procedure%20at%20Nuremberg%2C%20which%20relied%20on%20documentary%20evidence%20%E2%80%93%20against%20the%20perpetrator%20in%20the%20latter%E2%80%99s%20physical%20presence%20marked%20the%20verbal%20%3Cem%3Ecorpus%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3Edelicti%3C%2Fem%3E%20of%20and%20from%20the%20times%20of%20horror.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20trial%20is%20also%20a%20spectacle%20where%20the%20survivors%E2%80%99%20memories%20go%20up%20against%20those%20of%20the%20perps.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20the%20testimony%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Fcambodia-horror-20-years-after-pol-pots-death%5C%22%3EVann%20Nath%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20survived%20S-21%2C%20gave%20the%20lie%20to%20the%20denials%20and%20evasions%20of%20Kaing%20Guek%20Eav%2C%20aka%20%E2%80%98Duch%E2%80%99%2C%20the%20commandant%20of%20S-21%2C%20at%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eccc.gov.kh%2Fen%2Fnode%2F39457%5C%22%3EKhmer%20Rouge%20trials%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20defence%20stated%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDuch%20was%20just%20a%20minor%20Secretary%20who%20had%20no%20real%20authority%20to%20make%20decisions%20or%20to%20do%20anything%20contradictory%20to%20the%20directions%20from%20or%20the%20orders%20from%20the%20upper%20echelon.%20Therefore%20he%20could%20not%20be%20considered%20the%20most%20responsible%20person.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20own%20apology%2C%20Duch%20said%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20the%20director%20of%20S-21%2C%20I%20did%20not%20dare%20to%20seek%20any%20alternatives%20to%20obeying%20the%20orders%20from%20the%20upper%20echelon%2C%20despite%20knowing%20that%20carrying%20them%20out%20would%20lead%20to%20the%20loss%20of%20thousands%20of%20lives.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20claimed%20that%20he%20was%20not%20present%20at%20the%20tortures%2C%20and%20did%20not%20even%20hear%20the%20screams%20of%20the%20tortured.%20But%20survivors%20like%20Nath%20testified%20to%20his%20presence%2C%20and%20thereby%20pointed%20to%20the%20manipulation%20of%20chronology%2C%20cause%2C%20and%20memory%20by%20the%20accused.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%2C%20what%20is%20also%20on%20trial%20in%20the%20form%20of%20the%20victims%E2%80%99%20testimony%20is%20the%20public%20secret%20of%20murders%2C%20kidnappings%2C%20and%20disappearances.%20Cross-examinations%2C%20as%20in%20the%20case%20of%20the%20Cambodia%20trials%2C%20bring%20together%20private%20victim%20testimony%2C%20perpetrator%20testimony%2C%20and%20historical%20records.%20The%20trial%20gives%20the%20public%20secret%2C%20available%20to%20many%20as%20personal%20or%20even%20shared%20memories%2C%20a%20visible%20form%20with%20images%2C%20documentation%2C%20interviews%2C%20etc.%20This%20transforms%20the%20public%20secret%20into%20public%20archivisation%20%E2%80%93%20a%20process%20in%20which%20the%20perp%20is%20%3Cem%3Epresent%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20although%20s%2Fhe%20may%20have%20been%20behind%20the%20scenes%2C%20%E2%80%98merely%E2%80%99%20ordering%20the%20heinous%20acts%20when%20they%20were%20undertaken.%20The%20public%20archivisation%20project%20is%20often%20framed%20within%20the%20principles%20of%20law%2C%20memory%2C%20and%20accountability.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20two%20aspects%20to%20this%20public%20archivisation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20common%20sense%20tells%20us%20that%20perps%20on%20trial%20minimise%20their%20role%20in%20the%20genocides%20and%20massacres%2C%20and%20claim%20to%20be%20either%20simply%20following%20orders.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20can%20we%20call%20what%20the%20perpetrator%20states%20in%20court%20%E2%80%98testimony%E2%80%99%20or%20is%20s%2Fhe%20manipulating%20the%20memories%20to%20provide%20a%20different%20genealogy%20of%20the%20events%20%E2%80%93%20one%20in%20which%20s%2Fhe%20had%20little%20or%20no%20role%3F%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjournals.openedition.org%2Ftemoigner%2F5249%3Flang%3Den%5C%22%3EAnneleen%20Spiessens%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20argued%20that%20%E2%80%98the%20very%20possibility%20of%20the%20killer%E2%80%99s%20testimony%20is%20disquieting.%20How%20can%20a%20person%20be%20capable%20of%20telling%20this%20kind%20of%20story%20and%20voicing%20the%20ultimate%20transgression%3F%E2%80%99%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESecond%2C%20when%20the%20perpetrators%20die%20before%20such%20a%20public%20archivisation%20process%20where%2C%20very%20often%2C%20they%20are%20called%20upon%20to%20confess%2C%20many%20like%20Videla%20carry%20their%20dark%20secrets%20to%20the%20grave%20and%20thus%20resist%20publicisation.%20For%20critics%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tandfonline.com%2Fdoi%2Fabs%2F10.1080%2F13642987.2015.1032263%5C%22%3EMichelle%20Caswell%20and%20Anne%20Gilliland%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20deaths%20of%20the%20perpetrators%20means%20they%20escape%20this%20process%20entirely.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20accused%20become%20forever-from-now-on%20unavailable%20and%20thus%20unassailable%20evidence%20%E2%80%93%20in%20essence%3B%20they%20are%20transformed%20into%20imagined%20documents%20that%20can%20never%20be%20cross-examined.%20In%20this%20construction%2C%20the%20would-be%20testimony%20of%20perpetrators%20is%20given%20epistemological%20validity%20over%20that%20of%20victims%2C%20offering%20up%20the%20false%20and%20unfulfillable%20promise%20of%20establishing%20a%20singular%20truth.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20victim%20testifies%20while%20the%20perpetrator%20confesses%2C%20writes%20perpetrator-and-film-studies%20theorist%20Raya%20Morag.%20But%20what%20happens%20where%20there%20is%20%3Cem%3Eno%3C%2Fem%3E%20confession%2C%20she%20argues.%20Caswell%20and%20Gilliland%20note%20that%20with%20their%20deaths%2C%20no%20cross-examination%20of%20the%20perp%20is%20possible%2C%20and%20one%20can%20only%20speculate%20on%20their%20intentions%20and%20psychological%20make-up.%20We%20imagine%20them%20as%20documents%20that%20provide%20a%20certain%20historical%20memory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20perhaps%2C%20there%20is%20a%20third%20way%20of%20looking%20at%20the%20public%20archivisation%20and%20memorialisation%20of%20perpetrator%20testimonies.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjpr.winchesteruniversitypress.org%2Farticles%2F10.21039%2Fjpr.v1i1.38%5C%22%3ESibylle%20Schmidt%3C%2Fa%3E%20argues%20that%20the%20perps%20are%20%3Cem%3Eauctor%20delicti%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20author%20or%20originator%20of%20an%20act%2C%20in%20this%20case%2C%20of%20murders%20and%20killings.%20Schmidt%20writes%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20person%20is%20the%20author%20of%20a%20violent%20transformation%20of%20the%20state%20of%20the%20world%2C%20be%20it%20through%20his%20or%20her%20actions%20or%20omissions.%20The%20deed%20carries%2C%20so%20to%20speak%2C%20his%20or%20her%20fingerprint.%20Perpetration%20has%20to%20do%20with%20authorship%20%E2%80%93%20even%20if%20structural%20political%20violence%20seeks%20to%20deny%20and%20conceal%20individual%20responsibility.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESchmidt%20brings%20together%20both%20testimonial%20narrative%20and%20memorialisation%20as-public%20archivisation%20here.%20Some%2C%20like%20Eichmann%2C%20Pol%20Pot%2C%20or%20Himmler%20may%20have%20been%20desk-murderers%2C%20issuing%20kill%20orders.%20Others%20like%20Duch%20were%20physically%20instrumental%20in%20carrying%20out%20the%20heinous%20acts%20%E2%80%93%20which%20the%20survivors%20recall%20at%20the%20trial.%20But%20both%20categories%20of%20perps%20are%20%3Cem%3Eauctor%20delicti%3C%2Fem%3E%20%E2%80%93%20they%20authored%20the%20acts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20third%C2%A0%20aspect%20is%20precisely%20why%20the%20bringing-to-trial%20%E2%80%93%20although%20it%20may%20not%20result%20in%20justice%20%E2%80%93%20is%20important.%20The%20trial%2C%20a%20public%20spectacle%2C%20is%20an%20act%20of%20public%20archivisation%20of%20the%20worst%20memories%20of%20a%20community%2C%20culture%2C%20and%20state.%20It%20points%20to%20the%20authorship%20of%20such%20acts%20that%20produced%20the%20various%20%3Cem%3Ecorpus%20delicti%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20even%20when%20the%20corpus%20is%20conspicuous%20by%20its%20%3Cem%3Eabsence%3C%2Fem%3E.%20The%20public%20archivization%20of%20both%20%3Cem%3Ecorpus%20delicti%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20the%20more%20troubling%20%3Cem%3Eauctor%20delicti%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20crucial%20not%20just%20for%20the%20past%20but%20also%20for%20the%20future%2C%20as%20illustrated%20by%20all%20such%20genocide%20trials.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20bring%20in%20and%20retain%20perp%20memories%20in%20the%20public%20eye%20is%20not%20about%20honouring%20them%20but%20to%20point%20to%20questions%20of%20authorship%2C%20of%20genealogy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%E2%80%98never%20again%E2%80%99%20slogan%20can%20only%20make%20sense%20when%20aligned%20with%20%E2%80%98never%20forget%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fpramod-k-nayar%5C%22%3EPramod%20K.%20Nayar%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0teaches%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Hyderabad.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704105033000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F01162813%2FIMG_2641.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fwhat-about-the-memory-of-perpetrators%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Should%20the%20corpses%20of%20the%20perpetrator%20be%20treated%20as%20corpus%20delicti%3F%20Does%20this%20corpse%2C%20of%20the%20perpetrator%2C%20bring%20about%20closure%20for%20survivors%20of%20those%20s%2Fhe%20had%20executed%3F%20Or%20does%20the%20very%20presence%20of%20the%20perpetrator%E2%80%99s%20corpse%2C%20often%20interred%20grandly%2C%20mark%20the%20transformation%20of%20the%20villain%20into%20a%20hero%3F%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fwhat-about-the-memory-of-perpetrators%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India%E2%80%99s%20Housing%20Boom%20Calls%20for%20Urgent%20Upgrade%20in%20Construction%20Practices%2C%20Labour%20Rights%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F16134843%2Fimage-1392.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20developers%E2%80%99%20decision%20to%20demolish%20the%20multi-storey%20towers%20at%20the%20Chintels%20Paradiso%20Housing%20complex%20in%20Gurgaon%20and%20in%20the%20Delhi%20Development%20Authority%E2%80%99s%20(DDA%E2%80%99s)%20Signature%20View%20Apartments%20in%20North%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20Mukherjee%20Nagar%20draws%20serious%20attention%20to%20the%20unfortunate%20state%20of%20the%20construction%20industry%20in%20India%20today.%20The%20newly%20built%20apartment%20structures%20have%20to%20be%20pulled%20down%20because%20of%20poor%20construction%20putting%20occupants%20lives%20at%20risk.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20proposal%20to%20demolish%20houses%20in%20both%20residential%20complexes%20has%20caused%20widespread%20concern%20amongst%20home%20buyers%20in%20the%20in%20and%20around%20Delhi.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EPeople%20who%20had%20invested%20their%20savings%20to%20buy%20a%20home%20that%20they%20intended%20to%20live%20in%20are%20not%20only%20sorely%20disappointed%2C%20but%20also%20angry%20at%20having%20waited%20for%20years%20to%20move%20into%20their%20apartments%20and%20then%20have%20their%20dreams%20shattered%20as%20their%20newly%20built%20apartments%20have%20to%20be%20evacuated%20and%20demolished.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBecause%20of%20poor%20construction%2C%20chunks%20of%20plaster%20had%20begun%20to%20fall%20in%20different%20parts%20of%20the%20DDA%20apartments%20while%20in%20the%20case%20of%20Chintels%20Paradiso%2C%20in%20one%20of%20the%20apartment%20blocks%2C%20a%20large%20part%20of%20the%20sixth%20floor%20had%20fallen%20down%20all%20the%20way%20to%20the%20first%20floor%2C%20killing%20two%20women%20residents%20and%20injuring%20a%20man.%20Home%20owners%20in%20both%20complexes%20now%20have%20to%20wait%20as%20the%20developers%20proceed%20to%20demolish%20the%20constructed%20buildings%2C%20and%20then%20go%20through%20the%20process%20of%20reconstructing%20them.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EResidents%20have%20been%20promised%20rental%20compensation%20until%20they%20are%20given%20possession%20of%20the%20newly%20constructed%20apartments.%20The%20terms%20offered%20by%20the%20two%20developers%2C%20DDA%20and%20Chintels%2C%20vary.%20The%20DDA%20is%20offering%20owners%20an%20added%20increase%20of%20around%2020%20sq.%20ft.%20in%20the%20balcony%20area%20of%20each%20apartment%20at%20a%20marginal%20increase%20in%20cost%20and%20some%20additional%20common%20facilities%2C%20whereas%20Chintels%E2%80%99%20offer%20has%20not%20seen%20any%20change.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOwners%20have%20accepted%20the%20proposal%20to%20rebuild%20the%20houses%20in%20both%20cases%20as%20the%20alternative%20of%20accepting%20a%20cash%20settlement%20would%20be%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20the%20cost%20of%20construction%20at%20the%20time%20of%20original%20sale%20which%20is%20much%20lower%20in%20comparison%20to%20the%20cost%20of%20construction%20today%20and%20is%20not%20acceptable%20to%20most%20owners.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20DDA%20started%20construction%20of%20the%2012%20apartment%20towers%20consisting%20of%20336%20residential%20units%20in%202007%20and%20completed%20them%20in%202011.%20Soon%20after%20taking%20possession%20in%202012%2C%20owners%20noticed%20minor%20cracks%20and%20structural%20defects%20appearing%20in%20the%20buildings.%20The%20first%20allottee%20entered%20his%20home%20to%20find%20that%20a%20part%20of%20the%20roof%20had%20caved%20in.%20Subsequently%2C%20ceiling%20plaster%20falling%20and%20cracks%20in%20beams%20and%20balconies%20was%20reported%20in%2026%20flats.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Fvideo-santosh-mehrotra-unemployment-unpaid-worker%5C%22%3EWatch%20%7C%20What%20India%E2%80%99s%20Growing%20Army%20of%20Unpaid%20Workers%20Means%20for%20It%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EResidents%20raised%20these%20issues%20with%20the%20DDA%20but%20received%20no%20positive%20response.%20In%20June%202022%2C%20DDA%20asked%20IIT%20Delhi%20and%20Shriram%20Laboratories%20to%20test%20the%20structural%20integrity%20of%20the%20buildings.%20IIT%20submitted%20their%20report%20in%20November%202022%20declaring%20the%20buildings%20unfit%20for%20occupation.%20The%20Residents%20Welfare%20Association%20(RWA)%20negotiated%20the%20matter%20with%20DDA%20and%20settled%20for%20evacuation%20and%20demolition%20of%20all%20structures%20to%20be%20followed%20by%20new%20construction%20of%20the%20flats%20exactly%20as%20they%20were%20before%20along%20with%20the%20addition%20of%20144%20high%20income%20group%20(HIG)%20flats%2C%20168%20economically%20weaker%20section%20(EWS)%20flats%20as%20well%20as%20a%20clubhouse%20and%20community%20centre.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EChintels%20Paradiso%20in%20Gurgaon%20consisting%20of%20nine%2C%2014%20storey%20towers%20each%20with%2060%20apartments%20was%20completed%20in%20two%20phases%20in%202016%20and%20in%202017.%20After%20the%20first%20few%20residents%20moved%20in%2C%20they%20observed%20structural%20issues%2C%20cracks%20in%20ceilings%20and%20balconies%2C%20tiles%20falling%20off%2C%20and%20deflection%20in%20some%20balconies.%20After%20a%20structural%20audit%20by%20IIT%2C%20two%20towers%20were%20declared%20unfit%20for%20occupation.%20In%20July%202021%2C%20in%20Tower%20H%E2%80%99s%20front%20lobby%2C%20a%20portion%20of%20the%20ceiling%20fell%20down.%20On%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20February%2010%2C%202022%2C%20the%20ceiling%20slab%20on%20the%20sixth%20floor%20of%20Tower%20D%20collapsed%20and%20fell%20all%20the%20way%20down%20to%20the%20first%20floor%20killing%20two%20women%20and%20injuring%20one%20man.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnother%20IIT%20report%20clearly%20stated%20that%20the%20towers%20were%20not%20safe%20for%20habitation%20because%20of%20the%20high%20chloride%20content%20in%20the%20concrete%20which%20caused%20corrosion%20of%20the%20steel%20bars%20and%20that%20all%20flats%20be%20vacated%20and%20demolished.%20Between%20April-July%202023%2C%20the%20builder%20provided%20two%20options%20to%20the%20affected%20residents%20%E2%80%93%20either%20buy%20back%20or%20accept%20total%20reconstruction%20of%20all%20apartment%20blocks.%20The%20offer%20to%20reconstruct%20was%20accepted.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20is%20responsible%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20worth%20exploring%20what%20really%20happened%20in%20terms%20of%20shortcomings%20in%20both%20these%20projects.%20How%20is%20it%20that%20the%20developers%20were%20not%20aware%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20architects%20and%20structural%20engineers%20were%20not%20effectively%20involved%20in%20the%20process%20of%20implementing%20the%20project%3F%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20accordance%20with%20their%20professional%20commitment%2C%20they%20were%20required%20to%20not%20only%20provide%20the%20necessary%20drawings%20and%20details%20but%20also%20systematically%20oversee%20the%20actual%20construction%20on%20a%20timely%20basis.%20Did%20the%20failures%20occur%20only%20because%20of%20faulty%20implementation%20on%20the%20part%20of%20the%20contractors%20responsible%20for%20the%20construction%3F%20To%20some%20extent%2C%20the%20responsibility%20falls%20on%20all%20the%20professionals%20involved.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20unskilled%20labour%20forms%20a%20large%20part%20of%20the%20construction%20team%2C%20close%20monitoring%20of%20the%20implementation%20process%20by%20the%20supervisory%20staff%20is%20of%20prime%20importance.%20Although%20the%20volume%20of%20construction%20work%20has%20been%20steadily%20increasing%20across%20the%20country%20since%20the%20mid-1970s%2C%20the%20training%20of%20skilled%20craftsmen%20for%20construction%20work%20is%20inadequate%20and%20has%20not%20kept%20pace.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20architects%20and%20structural%20engineers%20are%20mainly%20responsible%20for%20producing%20the%20necessary%20drawings%2C%20specifications%2C%20and%20bill%20of%20quantities%20relating%20to%20their%20projects%2C%20they%20also%20need%20to%20check%20the%20progress%20of%20construction%20at%20different%20stages%20to%20ensure%20that%20work%20is%20being%20implemented%20in%20accordance%20with%20the%20plans.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F23103952%2F3158023774_54f2900169_c.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22799%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F23103952%2F3158023774_54f2900169_c.jpg%20799w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F23103952%2F3158023774_54f2900169_c-300x241.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-664608%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22641%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Most%20of%20this%20so-called%20increase%20in%20%E2%80%98jobs%E2%80%99%20in%20agriculture%20since%202019%20is%20in%20%E2%80%98unpaid%20family%20labour%E2%80%99%2C%20a%20form%20of%20self-employment%20where%20women%2C%20youth%20and%20children%20join%20other%20family%20members%20to%20appear%20%E2%80%98employed%E2%80%99.%E2%80%99%20Photo%3A%20jasleen_kaur%2FFlickr%20(CC%20BY-SA%202.0)%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20case%20of%20the%20aforementioned%20housing%20projects%2C%20it%20is%20quite%20clear%20that%20there%20were%20serious%20defaults%20in%20ensuring%20that%20specifications%20and%20drawing%20details%20were%20properly%20implemented.%20To%20some%20extent%2C%20this%20is%20because%20architects%20and%20engineers%20are%20generally%20paid%20fees%20that%20barely%20cover%20their%20cost%20as%20a%20result%20of%20which%20they%20tend%20to%20cut%20corners.%20%3C%2Fspan%3EDDA%20and%20other%20government%20agencies%20make%20a%20provision%20of%2010%25%20or%20more%20to%20cover%20their%20in-house%20design%20and%20engineering%20costs%2C%20but%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20architect%E2%80%99s%20and%20engineer%E2%80%99s%20fees%2C%20they%20generally%20pay%203%25%20to%204%25%20or%20even%20less.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20building%20industry%20happens%20to%20be%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20employers%20of%20workers%20in%20the%20informal%20sector.%20The%20average%20cost%20of%20construction%20in%20India%20is%20one%20of%20the%20lowest%20in%20the%20world.%20This%20is%20largely%20due%20to%20the%20small%20component%20allocated%20to%20labour%20in%20the%20total%20building%20cost.%20If%20building%20skills%20are%20to%20be%20improved%2C%20the%20cost%20of%20all%20labour%20will%20need%20to%20be%20substantially%20increased%2C%20along%20with%20a%20focussed%20increase%20in%20the%20process%20of%20training%20craftsmen%20all%20over%20the%20country.%20This%20can%20only%20happen%20if%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20setting%20up%20a%20large%20number%20of%20craft%20training%20institutes%20in%20every%20state%2C%20construction%20contractors%20implementing%20projects%20above%20a%20certain%20size%20were%20required%2C%20by%20law%2C%20to%20set%20up%20necessary%20skill%20training%20camps%20at%20their%20building%20sites.%20They%20should%20also%20be%20required%20to%20employ%20a%20specific%20number%20of%20such%20trained%20craftsmen.%20The%20enforcement%20of%20such%20training%20programs%20will%20increase%20the%20number%20of%20trained%20craftsmen%20all%20across%20the%20country.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBuilders%2C%20who%20make%20the%20maximum%20profit%20from%20these%2C%20should%20be%20made%20directly%20responsible%20not%20only%20for%20developing%20skills%20but%20also%20to%20ensure%20safe%20conditions%20on%20building%20sites.%20They%20need%20to%20shift%20to%20updated%20construction%20methods%20along%20with%20ensuring%20job%20security%20for%20all%20workers.%20The%20system%20of%20daily%20wage%20labour%20being%20supplied%20by%20middlemen%20who%20do%20not%20really%20protect%20the%20workers%E2%80%99%20long-term%20interests%20needs%20to%20be%20done%20away%20with.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EConstruction%20industry%20needs%20a%20complete%20overhaul%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDespite%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20building%20industry%20has%20steadily%20grown%20over%20the%20years%20with%20more%20and%20more%20construction%20due%20to%20industrial%20growth%20and%20urban%20development%2C%20actual%20conditions%20on%20many%20building%20sites%20remain%20unsafe%20and%20primitive.%20It%20is%20common%20to%20see%20bamboo%20or%20wooden%20%3Cem%3Eballi%3C%2Fem%3E%20scaffolding%2C%20along%20with%20wooden%20ramps%2C%20tied%20together%20with%20ropes.%20Workers%20on%20such%20sites%2C%20including%20women%2C%20work%20without%20proper%20safety%20gear%20and%20harness%20and%20carry%20building%20materials%20like%20bricks%20and%20concrete%20on%20their%20heads.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccidents%20are%20frequent%20and%20workers%E2%80%99%20lives%20are%20at%20risk.%20But%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20any%20control%2C%20and%20because%20this%20system%20is%20cheap%2C%20contractors%20continue%20to%20avoid%20upgrading%20to%20save%20expense.%20This%20is%20a%20dangerous%20system%20that%20needs%20complete%20overhaul.%20This%20is%20possible%2C%20both%2C%20by%20the%20enactment%20of%20stringent%20laws%20as%20well%20as%20by%20training%20large%20numbers%20of%20skilled%20workers.%20The%20use%20of%20unskilled%20workers%20needs%20to%20be%20steadily%20reduced%2C%20and%20ultimately%20done%20away%20with%20completely%20across%20the%20nation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Fmgnregs-aadhaar-system-payment%5C%22%3EAll%20MGNREGS%20Wages%20to%20Be%20Paid%20Through%20Aadhaar-Linked%20System%20From%20Today%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20the%20level%20of%20construction%20skills%20currently%20available%2C%20most%20contractors%20are%20only%20equipped%20to%20safely%20build%20ground%20plus%20two%20floors%20in%20most%20parts%20of%20the%20country.%20In%20the%20present%20situation%2C%20for%20all%20buildings%20that%20are%20higher%20than%20that%2C%20we%20are%20taking%20a%20serious%20risk%20by%20building%20unsafe%20structures.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20all%20construction%20work%2C%20the%20use%20of%20tubular%20steel%20scaffolding%20properly%20bolted%20together%20along%20with%20mechanical%20hoists%20and%20lifts%20for%20vertical%20movement%20of%20crew%20and%20material%20must%20be%20made%20compulsory.%20Concrete%20mixers%20with%20flexible%20pipes%20for%20delivery%20of%20mixed%20concrete%20is%20also%20necessary.%20Safety%20conditions%20with%20the%20proper%20enclosure%20of%20all%20buildings%20under%20construction%20must%20be%20ensured.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20the%20implementation%20of%20such%20proposals%20all%20workers%20need%20to%20be%20trained.%20Along%20with%20this%2C%20traditional%20skills%20related%20to%20carpentry%2C%20woodwork%2C%20cutting%2C%20polishing%20and%20installation%20of%20stonework%2C%20welding%20of%20steel%2C%20etc.%20along%20with%20the%20use%20of%20new%20machines%20and%20improved%20tools%20need%20to%20be%20taught%20and%20implemented%20with%20short%20term%20courses.%20Needless%20to%20say%2C%20all%20workers%20on%20building%20sites%20should%20also%20be%20provided%20with%20proper%20uniforms%20and%20safety%20gear%20without%20which%20they%20should%20not%20be%20permitted%20on%20building%20sites.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20of%20the%20important%20aspects%20of%20improving%20building%20techniques%20is%20the%20need%20to%20train%20workmen%20and%20engineers%20in%20project%20management.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20involves%20proper%20coordination%20of%20different%20craft%20skills%20to%20ensure%20overall%20time%20and%20cost%20control%20with%20the%20help%20of%20pert%20charts%2C%20and%20the%20regular%20checking%20and%20upgrading%20of%20the%20different%20aspects%20of%20work%20on%20all%20building%20sites.%20Proper%20project%20management%20ultimately%20results%20in%20better%20construction%20at%20cheaper%20costs.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20also%20important%20to%20ensure%20the%20provision%20of%20proper%20living%20accommodation%20for%20workers%20when%20construction%20sites%20are%20far%20from%20the%20villages%20or%20the%20area%20where%20the%20construction%20crew%20lives.%20In%20all%20large-scale%20development%20projects%2C%20a%20separate%20area%20should%20be%20allocated%20for%20building%20a%20complex%20of%20affordable%20dwelling%20units%20in%20close%20proximity.%20In%20order%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20needs%20of%20skilled%20and%20unskilled%20workers%20and%20their%20families%20are%20taken%20care%20of%2C%20the%20entire%20complex%20along%20with%20community%20support%20facilities%20should%20be%20financed%20and%20maintained%20by%20the%20builders%20along%20with%20the%20provision%20of%20safe%20transportation%20to%20individual%20building%20sites.%20Support%20facilities%20like%20schools%2C%20health%20centres%20and%20informal%20sector%20shopping%20complexes%20should%20all%20be%20part%20of%20such%20organised%20low-income%20settlement.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Fwhy-development-of-skill-centres-is-essential-for-rural-development%5C%22%3E%20Why%20Development%20of%20Skill%20Centres%20Is%20Essential%20For%20Rural%20Development%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20proposal%20to%20provide%20living%20accommodation%20for%20workers%20on%20building%20sites%20is%20not%20new.%20This%20was%20a%20standard%20requirement%20of%20all%20large%20projects%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%20during%20the%20construction%20boom%20in%20the%201960s.%20All%20contractors%20had%20to%20provide%20proper%20living%20and%20support%20facilities%20for%20all%20the%20labour%20that%20they%20brought%20from%20overseas%20for%20construction%20projects.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20miserable%20conditions%20on%20most%20of%20our%20construction%20sites%20along%20with%20the%20exploitation%20of%20labour%20throughout%20the%20country%20continues%20unabated%20because%20of%20lack%20of%20government%20intervention%20and%20control.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EContractors%20must%20also%20be%20made%20responsible%20for%20the%20provision%20of%20crafts%20and%20skill%20training%20institutes%20which%20would%20provide%20training%20in%20construction%20related%20skills%2C%20along%20with%20separate%20courses%20or%20advanced%20training%20in%20IT-related%20construction%20systems.%20These%20should%20be%20permanent%20educational%20institutes%2C%20which%20would%20periodically%20be%20upgraded%20in%20relation%20to%20the%20latest%20available%20construction%20technology.%20Such%20crafts%20and%20skill%20training%20institutes%20may%20over%20time%20become%20self-supporting%2C%20maintaining%20a%20close%20link%20with%20the%20building%20industry.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20number%20of%20such%20institutions%20located%20in%20the%20rural%20areas%20of%20each%20state%20would%20help%20to%20not%20only%20provide%20employment%2C%20but%20also%20ensure%20proper%20and%20systematic%20development%20of%20all%20rural%20areas%20on%20a%20continuing%20basis%20in%20the%20future.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20GDP%20data%2C%20India%20is%20currently%20one%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20fastest%20growing%20major%20economies%20and%20is%20currently%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20a%20housing%20boom.%20The%20demand%20for%20housing%20is%20steadily%20increasing%20in%20most%20urban%20areas%20and%20is%20expected%20to%20grow%20even%20faster%20in%20the%20years%20ahead.%20The%20long-awaited%20boom%20has%20created%20millions%20of%20new%20jobs.%20This%20has%20come%20after%20six%20years%20of%20debt%20and%20pandemic-induced%20downturn%20before%20the%20construction%20sector%20began%20improving%20last%20year.%20It%20has%20been%20driven%20by%20a%20severe%20housing%20shortage%20in%20big%20cities%20along%20with%20strong%20population%20growth.%20Steadily%20rising%20incomes%20has%20also%20been%20responsible%20for%20the%20increase%20in%20housing%20demand.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAcross%20the%20country%20there%20was%20an%20urban%20housing%20shortage%20of%2019%20million%20housing%20units%20last%20year.%20According%20to%20government%20estimates%20this%20is%20expected%20to%20double%20by%202030.%20The%20construction%20sector%20has%20contributed%20significantly%20to%20economic%20growth%20and%20this%20is%20likely%20to%20continue%20over%20the%20next%20couple%20of%20years.%20As%20per%20some%20real%20estate%20consultants%2C%20despite%20an%20increase%20in%20prices%2C%20home%20sales%20in%20seven%20largest%20cities%20increased%20by%20over%2036%25%20over%20the%20last%20quarter.%20With%20this%20increased%20housing%20demand%2C%20this%20is%20the%20right%20time%20for%20the%20government%20to%20take%20steps%20to%20improve%20the%20quality%20of%20construction%20across%20the%20country.%20Improved%20construction%20quality%20will%20automatically%20lead%20to%20an%20increase%20in%20wages%20of%20construction%20workers%20along%20with%20a%20substantial%20increase%20in%20the%20size%20of%20the%20construction%20industry.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Franjitsibikhi%5C%22%3ERanjit%20Sabikhi%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20an%20architect%20and%20urban%20designer.%20He%20was%20formerly%20a%20Professor%20of%20Urban%20Design%20at%20the%20School%20of%20Planning%20and%20Architecture%2C%20Delhi.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704103213000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F16134843%2Fimage-1392.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Findias-housing-boom-calls-for-urgent-upgrade-in-construction-practices-labour-rights%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20miserable%20conditions%20on%20most%20of%20our%20construction%20sites%20along%20with%20the%20exploitation%20of%20labour%20throughout%20the%20country%20continues%20unabated%20because%20of%20lack%20of%20government%20intervention%20and%20control.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A15%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Findias-housing-boom-calls-for-urgent-upgrade-in-construction-practices-labour-rights%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Telangana%20Must%20Announce%20a%20Humane%20Prison%20Reform%20Policy%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F05%2F01171400%2Fjail-prison.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EA%20video%20circulating%20among%20long-term%20prisoners%20out%20on%20bail%20features%20Revanth%20Reddy%E2%80%99s%20interview%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DWnhfqfzN5-Y%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9COpen%20Heart%20with%20RK%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20July%202015.%20Revanth%20Reddy%20had%20then%20served%20time%20in%20a%20central%20prison%20as%20an%20undertrial%20prisoner%2C%20accused%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newindianexpress.com%2Fstates%2Fandhra-pradesh%2F2015%2Fjun%2F01%2FCash-for-vote-Scam-TDP-MLA-Revanth-Reddy-Gives-Murky-Twist-to-MLC-Poll-749301.html%5C%22%3Ebribery%20to%20legislators%20for%20voting%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%20the%20interview%2C%20he%20speaks%20of%20significant%20challenges%20faced%20by%20prisoners.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EInequality%20before%20law%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20had%20granted%20Revanth%20Reddy%20the%20status%20of%20a%20special%20prisoner%20in%20June%202015.%20The%20prison%20authorities%20appointed%20a%20life-sentenced%20prisoner%2C%20Nagaiah%2C%20a%20Dalit%2C%20as%20his%20cook%20and%20assistant.%20Oblivious%20to%20unequal%20class%20and%20caste%20status%20before%20the%20law%2C%20Revanth%20Reddy%20genuinely%20admires%20his%20common%20sense%20regarding%20the%20political%20developments%20in%20the%20state.%20In%20a%20land%20dispute%20with%20his%20uncle%2C%20Nagaiah%20accidentally%20caused%20the%20death%20of%20an%20infant.%20Consequently%2C%20he%20was%20serving%20a%20life%20sentence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20no%20doubt%20that%20the%20majority%20of%20offenders%20like%20him%20offend%20on%20a%20sudden%20provocation.%20The%20number%20of%20organised%20offenders%20is%20still%20relatively%20small%20in%20prisons.%20Organized%20offenses%20obviously%20require%20a%20fair%20amount%20of%20literacy%2C%20technological%20skill%2C%20and%20resourcefulness.%20Such%20resourcefulness%2C%20of%20course%2C%20helps%20them%20to%20escape%20from%20the%20penal%20system.%20Consequently%2C%20they%20constitute%20the%20smallest%20minority.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHardening%20attitude%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20we%20often%20demonstrate%20an%20indiscriminately%20tougher%20attitude%20towards%20the%20prisoners.%20This%20harshness%20has%20increased%20tremendously%20in%20Telangana%2C%20signalling%20the%20rise%20of%20a%20new%20power%20elite.%20The%20state%20has%20released%20life%20prisoners%20only%20twice%20in%20the%20last%20ten%20years.%20During%20the%20same%20period%2C%20they%20were%20released%20four%20times%20in%20the%20neighbouring%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpubluu.com%2Fflip-book%2F346034%2F793801%2Fpage%2F1%5C%22%3E2016%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%202020%2C%20Telangana%20released%20those%20who%20completed%20seven%20years%20of%20actual%20sentence%20with%20three%20more%20years%20of%20remission%20for%20their%20good%20behaviour.%20Although%20the%20policy%20was%20announced%20after%20a%20long%20break%2C%20many%20were%20not%20released.%20The%20reasons%20are%20many.%20Firstly%2C%20while%20it%20laid%20down%20five%20criteria%20to%20qualify%20for%20release%2C%20it%20exempted%2019%20categories%20of%20prisoners%20as%20disqualified.%20The%20exempted%20criteria%20include%20prisoners%E2%80%99%20indiscipline.%20Those%20who%20committed%20offences%20against%20women%2C%20children%2C%20NDPS%20Act%20and%20public%20servants%20were%20some%20of%20the%20categories%20declared%20ineligible.%20It%20is%20possible%20that%20Nagaiah%20is%20still%20languishing%20in%20jail%20as%20his%20offence%20is%20arbitrarily%20interpreted%20as%20committed%20against%20a%20child.%20The%20state%20declared%20that%20such%20prisoners%20will%20be%20released%20after%20completing%2018%20to%2024%20years%20of%20incarceration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpubluu.com%2Fflip-book%2F346034%2F793824%2Fpage%2F1%5C%22%3E2020%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20number%20of%20disqualifications%20for%20the%20release%20of%20prisoners%20had%20increased%20to%2028%20categories.%20It%20declared%20that%20those%20who%20committed%20offences%20against%20public%20servants%20and%20girls%20would%20be%20considered%20for%20release%20after%2020%20to%2024%20years.%20The%20state%20also%20announced%20that%20life%20convicts%20previously%20detained%20under%20preventive%20detention%20laws%20are%20not%20eligible%2C%20even%20after%20completing%2014%20years%20in%20prison.%20%C2%A0The%20impact%20of%20this%20policy%20will%20be%20felt%20deeper%20after%20a%20decade%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fpolitical-pulse%2Ftelangana-assembly-polls-detention-law-8997756%2F%5C%22%3Epreventive%20detentions%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20accused%20in%20all%20sorts%20of%20offences%20are%20increasingly%20invoked%20these%20days.%20For%20instance%2C%20the%20state%20detained%20393%20offenders%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fncrb.gov.in%2Fuploads%2Fnationalcrimerecordsbureau%2Fcustom%2Fpsiyearwise2022%2F1701613297PSI2022ason01122023.pdf%5C%22%3E2022%3C%2Fa%3E%20alone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConsequently%2C%20life%20prisoners%20have%20become%20deeply%20anxious%20and%20depressed.%20Previously%2C%20those%20who%20committed%20offences%20under%20the%20SC%20and%20ST%20(POA)%20Act%20were%20also%20barred%20from%20early%20release%2C%20but%20that%20is%20no%20longer%20a%20condition.%20It%20is%20not%20argued%20that%20those%20who%20offend%20against%20the%20marginalised%20should%20be%20jailed%20indefinitely.%20This%20is%20just%20to%20point%20out%20the%20changing%20political%20choices.%20But%20the%20irrational%20criteria%20for%20the%20release%20of%20prisoners%20must%20be%20removed%20to%20create%20a%20democratic%20and%20transparent%20method%20of%20reviewing%20their%20sentences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20no%20democratic%20process%20for%20releasing%20prisoners.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20reasons%20exist%20for%20subjecting%20the%20prisoners%20to%20such%20an%20autocratic%20process.%20The%20first%20reason%20is%20that%20the%20system%20lacks%20an%20imagination%20regarding%20what%20constitutes%20reformation%20among%20prisoners.%20Furthermore%2C%20it%20lacks%20a%20method%20for%20capturing%20the%20transformations%20that%20prisoners%20undergo.%20As%20a%20result%20of%20this%20lack%20of%20imagination%2C%20the%20sentence%20review%20board%2C%20which%20is%20responsible%20for%20reviewing%20the%20effectiveness%20of%20sentences%20every%20three%20months%20under%20the%20law%2C%20has%20not%20met%20for%20decades.%20Consequently%2C%20the%20state%20has%20been%20deciding%20releases%20solely%20based%20on%20the%20gravity%20of%20the%20committed%20crime.%20This%20implies%20that%20the%20system%20disregards%20the%20significance%20of%20depriving%20offenders%20of%20decades%20of%20freedom.%20It%20completely%20overlooks%20the%20goal%20of%20transforming%20the%20prisoners.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPrison%20offers%20perspective%20to%20everyone%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20interview%2C%20Revanth%20Reddy%20said%20that%20a%20month%E2%80%99s%20imprisonment%20has%20put%20his%20life%20in%20perspective%20and%20set%20his%20life%E2%80%99s%20direction.%20This%20is%20true%20even%20for%20ordinary%20prisoners.%20Years%20of%20imprisonment%20provide%20a%20direction%20to%20their%20lives.%20They%20can%E2%80%99t%20help%20but%20wonder%20about%20the%20fate%20of%20their%20lives.%20Their%20indefinite%20prison%20terms%20definitely%20tell%20them%20early%20on%20why%20their%20lives%20have%20taken%20wrong%20turns.%20Many%20prisoners%20realise%20that%20they%20can%20remain%20sane%20only%20by%20engaging%20in%20nonstop%20work.%20Deeply%20melancholic%2C%20they%20experience%20a%20sea%20change%20in%20their%20attitudes.%20However%2C%20the%20system%20does%20not%20create%20opportunities%20to%20get%20back%20to%20normal%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAre%20prisoners%20a%20source%20of%20cheap%20labour%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERevanth%20Reddy%20further%20speaks%20about%20how%20the%20prisoners%20were%20paid%20just%20Rs.%2030%20per%20day%20as%20wages.%20While%20it%20has%20been%20increased%20to%20Rs%2070%20now%2C%20Karnataka%20pays%20prisoners%20Rs%20663%20per%20day%2C%20Delhi%20Rs%20308%2C%20AP%20and%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Rs%20200%2C%20Puducherry%20Rs.%20180%2C%20Bihar%20Rs%20156%2C%20and%20Odisha%20Rs%20145.%20The%20value%20of%20goods%20produced%20per%20inmate%20in%20Telangana%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fncrb.gov.in%2Fuploads%2Fnationalcrimerecordsbureau%2Fcustom%2Fpsiyearwise2022%2F1701613297PSI2022ason01122023.pdf%5C%22%3ERs%2052%2C331%3C%2Fa%3E%20per%20year%2C%20which%20is%20second%20highest%20after%20Tamil%20Nadu.%20The%20revenues%20of%20the%20state%20from%20the%20prisons%20have%20soared%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftsprisons.gov.in%2FEOI.pdf%5C%22%3ERs%20800%20crore%3C%2Fa%3E%20per%20year%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20wage%20paid%20in%20Telangana%20is%20difficult%20to%20justify%20by%20any%20standards.%20It%20is%20impossible%20to%20support%20their%20families%20with%20the%20meagre%20earnings.%20They%20save%20only%20Rs%2040%2C000-80%2C000%20after%20a%20decade%20of%20sweating.%20They%20allege%20that%20the%20government%20tightened%20the%20criteria%20for%20their%20release%20as%20the%20revenues%20from%20their%20labor%20soared.%20Revanth%20Reddy%E2%80%99s%20government%20needs%20to%20examine%20the%20ethical%20implications%20of%20treating%20prisoners%20as%20cheap%20labour.%20Why%20can%E2%80%99t%20the%20state%20pay%20them%20an%20amount%20equivalent%20to%20the%20value%20of%20their%20labour%3F%20Instead%20of%20considering%20them%20as%20a%20source%20of%20cheap%20labour%2C%20thoughtful%20consideration%20must%20be%20given%20to%20their%20rights%2C%20their%20potential%20for%20reintegration%20into%20society%2C%20and%20the%20overall%20goals%20of%20a%20fair%20and%20equitable%20criminal%20justice%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPreserving%20social%20status%20quo%20is%20reformation%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERevanth%20Reddy%20casually%20points%20out%20another%20thing%3A%20the%20prison%20authorities%20identify%20the%20professional%20experiences%20of%20the%20offenders%20%E2%80%93%20gardening%2C%20cooking%2C%20and%20haircutting%20%E2%80%93%20outside%20and%20assign%20them%20such%20jobs.%20It%20is%20unnecessary%20here%20to%20remind%20readers%20of%20the%20relationship%20between%20professions%20and%20castes.%20This%20has%20been%20happening%20in%20all%20the%20jails%20for%20the%20last%20two%20centuries.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Findia-prisons-caste-labour-segregation%5C%22%3Einvestigative%20report%20in%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20how%20caste%20governs%20prisons%20in%20Rajasthan%20has%20led%20to%20amendments%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fcaste-prison-rajasthan-high-court-prison-manual-suo-motu%5C%22%3Eprison%20manuals%3C%2Fa%3E%20recently.%20Revanth%20Reddy%20must%20examine%20whether%20this%20relationship%20between%20caste%20and%20nature%20of%20work%20has%20been%20influencing%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20attitude%20towards%20low%20wages%20for%20prisoners.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EReview%20prison%20practices%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUntil%201984%2C%20politicians%20involved%20in%20the%20political%20feuds%20of%20Rayalaseema%20and%20the%20Naxalites%20were%20imprisoned%20in%20sizeable%20numbers.%20The%20governments%20had%20a%20stake%20in%20releasing%20them%20within%20five%20years.%20Since%201994%2C%20they%20started%20releasing%20them%20after%20completion%20of%20seven%20years%20as%20prisoners.%20These%20generosities%20were%20by%20default%20extended%20to%20ordinary%20prisoners.%20The%20strong%20rights%20movements%20were%20also%20vocal%20on%20the%20rights%20of%20prisoners.%20Their%20gradual%20weakening%20has%20left%20the%20prisoners%20defenceless.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EImplications%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndefinite%20sentences%20for%20public%20protection%20in%20the%20US%20is%20considered%20as%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Flaw%2F2020%2Fdec%2F03%2Findefinite-sentences-the-greatest-single-stain-on-justice-system%5C%22%3Esingle%20greatest%20stain%20on%20the%20criminal%20justice%20system.%3C%2Fa%3E%20The%20government%20must%20understand%20the%20ethical%20implications%20of%20these%20%E2%80%98never-ending%20sentences%E2%80%99%20on%20the%20prisoners.%20They%20create%20uncertainties%20for%20prisoners%20and%20their%20families.%20The%20lack%20of%20a%20specific%20date%20leads%20to%20a%20loss%20of%20hope%2C%20making%20it%20challenging%20to%20plan%20for%20their%20future.%20Without%20hope%2C%20what%20would%20induce%20them%20to%20motivate%20them%20to%20improve%20themselves%3F%20Indefinite%20sentences%20are%20a%20form%20of%20cruel%20and%20inhumane%20treatment%20of%20prisoners.%20This%20does%20not%20offer%20opportunity%20for%20their%20reintegration.%20The%20uncertainty%20damages%20their%20sanity%20and%20well-being.%20Given%20the%20pervasive%20inequalities%2C%20indefinite%20sentences%20impact%20certain%20sections%20of%20society%20more%20than%20others.%20The%20Congress%20government%2C%20which%20claims%20to%20restore%20democracy%20and%20civil%20rights%2C%20should%20comprehensively%20review%20prison%20policies%20and%20practices%20and%20their%20impact%20on%20the%20lives%20of%20prisoners.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EMurali%20Karnam%20teaches%20at%20NALSAR%20University%20of%20Law%2C%20Hyderabad.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704101414000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F05%2F01171400%2Fjail-prison.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Ftelangana-must-announce-a-humane-prison-reform-policy%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Telangana%20Congress%20government%20should%20review%20prison%20practices%20for%20a%20fair%20and%20transparent%20system%20that%20promotes%20prisoners%E2%80%99%20reintegration.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Ftelangana-must-announce-a-humane-prison-reform-policy%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Who%20is%20former%20'party%20prince'%20set%20to%20be%20Denmark's%20new%20king%20after%20queen's%20shock%20abdication%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704101280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F01%2F70x70%2Fskynews-frederik-denmark_6408886.jpg%3F20240101162328%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fcrown-prince-frederik-the-former-party-prince-who-is-set-to-become-denmarks-new-king-13040268%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%20the%20surprise%20abdication%20of%20his%20mother%20Queen%20Margrethe%20II%2C%20Crown%20Prince%20Frederik%20of%20Denmark%20will%20ascend%20to%20the%20throne%20on%2014%20January.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A98%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fcrown-prince-frederik-the-former-party-prince-who-is-set-to-become-denmarks-new-king-13040268%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fcrown-prince-frederik-the-former-party-prince-who-is-set-to-become-denmarks-new-king-13040268%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fcrown-prince-frederik-the-former-party-prince-who-is-set-to-become-denmarks-new-king-13040268%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20Selection%20of%20Rabindranath%20Tagore%E2%80%99s%20Wide%20Variety%20of%20Work%2C%20All%20Collected%20in%20a%20Single%20Volume%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F06%2F06111059%2Fdiscover.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3ERabindranath%20Tagore%20was%20a%20many-sided%20genius%2C%20who%20dominated%20the%20cultural%20landscape%20of%20Bengal%20during%20the%20late%2019th%C2%A0and%20early%2020th%20centuries.%20His%20output%20was%20prolific%2C%20flowing%20through%20poetry%2C%20song%2C%20novels%2C%20short%20stories%2C%20plays%2C%20essays%20and%20paintings.%20A%20century%20later%2C%20his%20work%20still%20stirs%20the%20hearts%20and%20minds%20of%20Bengali-speaking%20people%20across%20the%20world.%20However%2C%20Rabindranath%20was%20much%20more%20than%20a%20Bengali%20poet.%20He%20belonged%20to%20India.%20His%20writings%20embody%20a%20deep%20knowledge%20of%20Indian%20history%2C%20civilisation%2C%20culture%2C%20philosophy%2C%20and%20traditions.%20As%20a%20public%20intellectual%2C%20he%20addressed%20major%20social%20and%20political%20issues%20of%20his%20time.%20As%20an%20educationist%2C%20he%20established%20rural%20schools%20and%20also%20the%20Visva%20Bharati%20University%20as%20an%20%E2%80%9Cinternational%20centre%20of%20humanistic%20values%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETagore%20wrote%20mainly%20in%20Bengali%2C%20and%20his%20work%20spanned%20many%20genres%20and%20thousands%20of%20pages.%20Though%20translations%20exist%2C%20the%20wide%20range%20of%20his%20work%20has%20not%20been%20accessible%20in%20a%20compact%20form%20to%20non-Bengali%20readers.%20A%20new%20book%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Best%20of%20Tagore%3C%2Fem%3E%20edited%20and%20introduced%20by%20Rudrangshu%20Mukherjee%2C%20presents%20a%20diverse%20selection%20of%20Tagore%E2%80%99s%20work%2C%20in%20English%2C%20collected%20in%20an%20elegant%20volume%20of%20about%20800%20pages.%20The%20book%20contains%20selected%20short%20stories%2C%20a%20novel%2C%20plays%2C%20essays%2C%20poems%20written%20for%20children%2C%20songs%2C%20and%20poetry.%20A%20few%20of%20the%20pieces%20were%20originally%20written%20in%20English%20by%20Tagore%20or%20were%20translated%20by%20him.%20But%20the%20majority%20is%20translations%20by%20other%20authors%20that%20have%20been%20published%20earlier.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20introduction%20by%20Rudrangshu%20Mukherjee%20provides%20a%20short%20biography%20of%20Rabindranath%20Tagore%20(1861%E2%80%931941).%20A%20well-researched%20table%20details%20the%20main%20personal%20events%20in%20each%20year%20of%20Tagore%E2%80%99s%20life.%20It%20also%20lists%20the%20major%20literary%20publications%20by%20other%20authors%20and%20the%20major%20historical%20events%20that%20occurred%20in%20that%20year.%20This%20provides%20a%20valuable%20backdrop%20for%20understanding%20the%20man%20and%20the%20context%20of%20his%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20early%20twenties%2C%20Rabindranath%20travelled%20extensively%20in%20East%20Bengal%20(now%20Bangladesh)%2C%20managing%20his%20family%20estates.%20This%20exposure%20profoundly%20influenced%20his%20creativity%20and%20social%20conscience.%20Tagore%20was%20moved%20by%20the%20beauty%20of%20nature.%20He%20also%20observed%20the%20difficult%20lives%20of%20ordinary%20people.%20These%20themes%20found%20expression%20in%20many%20of%20his%20famous%20short%20stories%20and%20poems.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%201905%2C%20Rabindranath%20became%20politically%20active.%20He%20opposed%20Curzon%E2%80%99s%20plan%20to%20communally%20divide%20Bengal.%20Tagore%20supported%20the%20%E2%80%98swadeshi%E2%80%99%20movement%20but%20rejected%20the%20use%20of%20coercion%20to%20enforce%20the%20boycott%20of%20foreign%20goods.%20Nationalism%20became%20a%20recurrent%20theme%20in%20his%20writing.%20By%201906%2C%20he%20advocated%20initiatives%20for%20improving%20the%20welfare%20of%20the%20villagers.%20In%20his%20own%20family%20estates%2C%20he%20established%20free%20health%20centres%2C%20primary%20schools%2C%20adult%20education%20classes%20at%20night%2C%20and%20also%20a%20rural%20bank%20to%20fight%20moneylenders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20depth%20and%20variety%20of%20the%20writings%20included%20in%20this%20book%20provide%20a%20comprehensive%20exposure%20to%20Tagore%E2%80%99s%20creative%20endeavours%20from%20different%20phases%20of%20his%20life.%20However%2C%20one%20may%20ask%3A%20Why%20read%20Tagore%20today%3F%C2%A0%20Is%20he%20relevant%20to%20our%20life%20and%20times%3F%20From%20this%20perspective%2C%20Rabindranath%E2%80%99s%20writings%20can%20be%20broadly%20classified%20as%20follows%3A%20(a)%20Those%20that%20do%20not%20belong%20to%20any%20era%3B%20(b)%20Those%20that%20reflect%20a%20particular%20historical%20period%20and%20society%3B%20and%20(c)%20Those%20that%20address%20grand%20themes%20like%20civilisation%2C%20nationalism%20and%20philosophy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20301px)%2085vw%2C%20301px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F01134418%2F9158SqaopUL._AC_UF10001000_QL80_.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22301%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F01134418%2F9158SqaopUL._AC_UF10001000_QL80_.jpg%20610w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F01134418%2F9158SqaopUL._AC_UF10001000_QL80_-183x300.jpg%20183w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-691182%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22493%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20Best%20of%20Tagore%3Cbr%3EEdited%20by%20Rudrangshu%20Mukherjee%3Cbr%3EEveryman%E2%80%99s%20Library%2C%202023%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20songs%20and%20poems%20belong%20to%20the%20first%20category.%20Tagore%E2%80%99s%20songs%20are%20of%20exquisite%20lyrical%20beauty%20and%20their%20themes%20(love%2C%20nature%E2%80%99s%20beauty%2C%20the%20changing%20seasons%2C%20prayer%2C%20sorrow%20and%20hope)%20transcend%20time%20and%20place.%20Tagore%20composed%20over%202200%20songs.%20He%20said%20that%20many%20of%20them%20arose%20in%20him%20spontaneously.%20The%20book%20contains%20the%20translations%20of%2030%20of%20his%20best-known%20songs.%20Of%20all%20his%20writings%2C%20however%2C%20the%20songs%20are%20the%20most%20difficult%20to%20translate.%20In%20the%20original%2C%20the%20words%20and%20music%20blend%20magically.%20Their%20beauty%20transports%20the%20listener%20to%20another%20plane%20of%20awareness.%20It%20is%20extremely%20difficult%20to%20convey%20the%20subtle%20nuances%20and%20emotive%20content%20of%20these%20songs%20in%20English.%20Hence%2C%20it%20may%20be%20a%20good%20idea%20to%20provide%20web%20links%20to%20the%20original%20songs%20that%20are%20available%20online.%20Readers%20of%20the%20translated%20lyrics%20would%20appreciate%20them%20more%20fully%20by%20hearing%20them%20sung.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%2046%20poems%20in%20the%20book.%20They%20are%20powerful%20and%20beautiful.%20Their%20themes%20vary.%20I%20will%20comment%20on%20a%20few%20to%20convey%20their%20flavour.%20%E2%80%98The%20Spring%20Wakes%20from%20Its%20Dream%E2%80%99%20is%20famous.%20It%20records%20the%20poet%E2%80%99s%20actual%20spiritual%20experience%20in%20his%20teens%2C%20which%20awakened%20the%20fountain%20of%20his%20creativity.%20%E2%80%98I%20Won%E2%80%99t%20Let%20You%20Go%E2%80%99%20is%20a%20poignant%20poem%20about%20a%20little%20daughter%E2%80%99s%20reluctance%20to%20let%20her%20father%20leave.%20The%20poet%20sees%20in%20the%20little%20girl%E2%80%99s%20cry%20a%20reflection%20of%20the%20eternal%20contest%20between%20love%20and%20inevitable%20farewell%20that%20resonates%20through%20all%20creation.%20Some%20poems%20are%20patriotic.%20%E2%80%98Now%20Turn%20Me%20Back%E2%80%99%20highlights%20the%20poet%E2%80%99s%20role%20in%20a%20time%20of%20political%20struggle.%20The%20poet%20must%20sacrifice%20for%20the%20cause.%20He%20%E2%80%9Cmust%20walk%20life%E2%80%99s%20thorny%20path%20silent%2C%20alone%2C%20patient%20through%20joy%20and%20grief.%E2%80%9D%20In%20the%20iconic%20poem%20%E2%80%98Where%20the%20Mind%20Is%20Without%20Fear%E2%80%99%2C%20Tagore%20articulates%20his%20vision%20for%20independent%20India%E2%80%94free%20and%20fearless%2C%20independent%20yet%20open%20to%20the%20world%2C%20grounded%20in%20truth%20and%20justice%2C%20and%20shunning%20petty%20divisions.%20In%20%E2%80%98Pilgrimage%20to%20India%E2%80%99%2C%20Tagore%20sees%20India%E2%80%99s%20grand%20civilisational%20role%20as%20a%20great%20unifier%20of%20humanity.%20On%20India%E2%80%99s%20sacred%20shore%2C%20the%20poet%20says%2C%20down%20the%20ages%20successive%20waves%20of%20different%20races%20have%20arrived.%20India%20has%20absorbed%20them%20all%20and%20unified%20them.%20Her%20inclusive%20mission%2C%20to%20forge%20a%20common%20humanity%2C%20still%20continues.%20%E2%80%98The%20Flying%20Geese%E2%80%99%20(Balaka)%20is%20profound.%20Beside%20the%20Jhelum%20River%2C%20in%20the%20hushed%20twilight%E2%80%94the%20immense%20silence%20is%20suddenly%20broken.%20A%20flock%20of%20geese%20streaks%20across%20the%20evening%20sky.%20The%20sound%20of%20their%20fluttering%20wings%20transports%20the%20poet%20spiritually.%20He%20perceives%20the%20universal%20longing%20in%20all%20creation%20to%20merge%20with%20the%20infinite.%20There%20are%20many%20more%20poems%20here%20to%20delight%20the%20reader.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20second%20category%20are%20his%20short%20stories%2C%20plays%20and%20novels.%20This%20volume%20contains%20seventeen%20short%20stories.%20A%20few%2C%20like%20Kabuliwallah%2C%20The%20Post%20Master%2C%20and%20The%20Hungry%20Stones%20have%20inspired%20award-winning%20movies.%20These%20stories%20reflect%20the%20social%20conditions%20of%20Bengal%20in%20that%20period.%20Tagore%E2%80%99s%20keen%20power%20of%20observation%2C%20his%20sympathy%20for%20ordinary%20folk%20coping%20with%20life%E2%80%99s%20difficulties%2C%20his%20depiction%20of%20the%20social%20relations%20between%20master%20and%20servant%2C%20of%20the%20rigidity%20of%20social%20customs%20paint%20a%20vivid%20picture%20of%20rural%20life%20in%20late%2019%3Csup%3Eth%3C%2Fsup%3E%20century%20Bengal.%20In%20many%20of%20the%20stories%2C%20the%20central%20characters%20are%20girls%20and%20women%20who%20confront%20social%20obstacles.%C2%A0%20%E2%80%98The%20Ghat%E2%80%99s%20Story%E2%80%99%20is%20about%20a%20sweet%20young%20girl%2C%20Kusum.%20She%20is%20married%20off%20as%20a%20child%2C%20is%20widowed%20early%20and%20returns%20to%20her%20village.%20But%20after%20the%20disgrace%20of%20widowhood%2C%20as%20she%20grows%20to%20be%20a%20beautiful%20woman%2C%20there%20are%20no%20options%20for%20her%20to%20experience%20normal%20emotions.%20%E2%80%98The%20Post-Master%E2%80%99%20is%20about%20a%20young%2C%20orphaned%20girl.%20She%20works%20as%20a%20domestic%20servant%20for%20an%20urban%20young%20man%20who%20is%20appointed%20a%20postmaster%20in%20her%20village.%20He%20is%20lonely%20and%20a%20misfit%20in%20rural%20society.%20The%20two%20form%20a%20sweet%2C%20innocent%2C%20almost%20brother-sisterly%20friendship.%20He%20starts%20teaching%20her.%20She%20takes%20care%20of%20him%20when%20he%20is%20ill.%20However%2C%20when%20he%20leaves%20the%20village%2C%20the%20power%20of%20the%20social%20barrier%20between%20them%20becomes%20apparent.%20The%20simple%20girl%E2%80%99s%20human%20feelings%20are%20real%2C%20but%20his%20attitude%20remains%20fundamentally%20transactional.%20%E2%80%98The%20Living%20and%20the%20Dead%E2%80%99%20is%20a%20strange%20tale%20about%20a%20young%20widow%2C%20who%20lives%20with%20her%20relatives.%20She%20loses%20consciousness%20and%20is%20mistakenly%20presumed%20dead.%20Her%20cremation%20is%20delayed%20inadvertently.%C2%A0%20She%20wakes%20up%20alone%20and%20escapes%20unnoticed%20from%20the%20unlit%20pyre.%20However%2C%20when%20she%20finally%20returns%20to%20her%20relatives%2C%20she%20finds%20it%20impossible%20to%20convince%20them%20that%20she%20is%20actually%20alive.%20The%20story%20reveals%20that%20identity%20and%20status%20are%20socially%20conferred.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%98The%20Little%20Master%E2%80%99s%20Return%E2%80%99%2C%20portrays%20the%20feudal%20relationship.%20Raicharan%20is%20a%20devoted%20servant%20in%20a%20wealthy%20household.%20He%20has%20served%20the%20young%20son%20of%20the%20family%20since%20latter%E2%80%99s%20childhood.%20The%20young%20man%20eventually%20becomes%20the%20head%20of%20the%20family%2C%20marries%20and%20has%20a%20son.%20Raicharan%20is%20asked%20to%20look%20after%20the%20zamindar%E2%80%99s%20little%20son.%20He%20does%20so%20with%20love%20and%20zeal.%20Unfortunately%2C%20the%20child%20drowns%20accidentally%20while%20in%20his%20care.%20Raicharan%20departs%20for%20his%20village.%20Soon%2C%20he%20has%20a%20son%20of%20his%20own%2C%20but%20loses%20his%20wife.%20He%20brings%20the%20child%20up%20like%20a%20%E2%80%98little%20master%E2%80%99.%20Having%20exhausted%20his%20resources%2C%20Raicharan%20finally%20takes%20the%20boy%20to%20the%20zamindar%E2%80%99s%20home%20and%20claims%20that%20he%20had%20abducted%20the%20zamindar%E2%80%99s%20child.%20His%20story%20is%20believed.%20The%20young%20boy%20is%20accepted%20by%20the%20zamindar%2C%20but%20Raicharan%20is%20kicked%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20stories%20cast%20a%20critical%20eye%20on%20the%20behaviour%20of%20the%20urban%20wealthy%20class.%20%E2%80%98The%20Patriot%E2%80%99%20exposes%20the%20hypocrisy%20of%20a%20%E2%80%98patriot%E2%80%99%20who%20boycotts%20Western%20cloth%20and%20wears%20khaddar%20but%20refuses%20to%20help%20a%20sweeper%20who%20is%20being%20thrashed%20for%20accidentally%20touching%20an%20upper%20caste%20individual.%20%E2%80%98The%20Laboratory%E2%80%99%2C%20published%20in%201940%2C%20is%20a%20critique%20of%20urban%2C%20wealthy%20Bengal%20society.%20The%20characters%20push%20against%20traditional%20boundaries%20and%20customs.%20Tagore%20is%20candid%20in%20his%20description%20of%20sexuality%2C%20seduction%2C%20inter-caste%2C%20inter-community%20and%20extra-marital%20relationships.%20The%20society%20is%20amoral%2C%20decadent%2C%20and%20commercially%20driven%2C%20in%20which%20the%20characters%20are%20cunning%2C%20manipulative%20and%20dishonest.%20Tagore%20criticises%20the%20contemporary%20Bengali%20male%20through%20the%20personalities%20of%20key%20characters%E2%80%93a%20scientist%20who%20is%20studious%20but%20unworldly%20and%20weak%2C%20an%20engineer%20who%20is%20brilliant%20but%20corrupt%2C%20and%20a%20professor%20who%20gets%20sexually%20manipulated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20third%20major%20category%20of%20work%20are%20his%20essays.%20In%20these%20works%2C%20the%20author%20addresses%20major%20issues%20of%20his%20time.%20During%20the%201920s%20and%201930s%2C%20he%20travelled%20extensively%20and%20lectured%20in%20Asia%2C%20America%20and%20Europe%2C%20where%20he%20spoke%20against%20blind%20nationalism%2C%20war%20and%20violence.%20He%20articulated%20his%20views%20in%20essays%20on%20nationalism%2C%20colonialism%2C%20and%20the%20crisis%20of%20civilisation%2C%20several%20of%20which%20are%20included%20in%20this%20volume.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20these%20essays%20were%20written%20a%20century%20ago%2C%20they%20remain%20surprisingly%20relevant.%20Tagore%E2%80%99s%20message%20of%20universal%20humanism%20and%20cultural%20understanding%20is%20inspiring%20and%20thought%20provoking.%20A%20core%20argument%20running%20through%20them%20is%20that%20man%20is%20primarily%20a%20moral%20creature.%C2%A0%20Morality%20is%20grounded%20in%20affinity%20with%20nature%2C%20community%2C%20social%20bonds%20and%20cooperation.%20India%2C%20he%20says%2C%20should%20abandon%20the%20social%20customs%20of%20the%20caste%20system%20%E2%80%9Cthat%20generated%20a%20want%20of%20self-respect%E2%80%9D%20and%20also%20the%20%E2%80%9Clazy%20habit%20of%20relying%20upon%20the%20authority%20of%20traditions%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20when%20societies%20are%20mobilised%20into%20machines%20for%20material%20aggrandisement%20and%20organised%20aggression%2C%20a%20%E2%80%9Cdense%2C%20poisonous%20atmosphere%20of%20world-wide%20suspicion%20and%20greed%20and%20panic%E2%80%9D%20is%20created.%20Colonized%20countries%20are%20exploited.%20But%20the%20rich%20also%20suffer%20by%20%E2%80%9Cbartering%20the%20higher%20aspirations%20of%20life%20for%20profit%20and%20power%E2%80%9D%20leading%20to%20the%20%E2%80%9Cwreckage%20of%20your%20soul%E2%80%9D%E2%80%A6In%20these%20conditions%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20moral%20man%20remains%20behind%E2%80%9D.%20Our%20task%2C%20according%20to%20Tagore%2C%20is%20to%20reclaim%20our%20full%20humanity.%20For%20people%20of%20different%20races%20to%20thrive%20together%2C%20we%20must%20acknowledge%20real%20differences%20where%20they%20exist%2C%20and%20yet%20seek%20a%20basis%20for%20unity.%20For%20this%2C%20Tagore%20recommends%20the%20message%20of%20great%20saints%20like%20Nanak%2C%20Kabir%2C%20and%20Chaitanya.%20Human%20beings%20will%20have%20to%20exert%20all%20their%20moral%20power%20of%20love%20and%20clarity%20of%20vision%20to%20comprehend%2C%20what%20Tagore%20terms%2C%20the%20%E2%80%9Cwhole%20world%20of%20men%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20much%20more%20in%20this%20volume%20and%20commend%20Rudrangshu%20Mukherjee%20for%20this%20excellent%20book.%20English%20readers%20will%20benefit%20from%20reading%20it%20and%20I%20recommend%20it%20wholeheartedly%20to%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EChiranjib%20Sen%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3E%20is%20distinguished%20Pprofessor%20in%20the%20School%20of%20Liberal%20Studies%20at%20the%20BML%20Munjal%20University.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704099632000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F06%2F06111059%2Fdiscover.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fa-selection-of-rabindranath-tagores-wide-variety-of-work-all-collected-in-a-single-volume%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Short%20stories%2C%20poems%20and%20essays%2C%20all%20translated%20in%20English%2C%20of%20the%20Nobel%20Prize%20winning%20writer%2C%20offer%20a%20glimpse%20into%20his%20vast%20and%20varied%20output.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A19%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fa-selection-of-rabindranath-tagores-wide-variety-of-work-all-collected-in-a-single-volume%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22