bear%2Fstatus%2F1741484018334613875%5C%22%3Ean%20FIR%20against%2018%20people%20including%20AISA%20and%20BCM%20members.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUP%20Congress%20President%20Ajay%20Rai%20had%20accused%20the%20BJP%20of%20being%20involved%20in%20the%20case%20in%20November.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20an%20FIR%20was%20filed%20against%20him%20and%20effigies%20of%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20were%20burnt%20by%20the%20ABVP%2C%20Zubair%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fzoo_bear%2Fstatus%2F1741484018334613875%5C%22%3Enoted%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20also%20added%20that%20Pandey%20and%20Patel%20were%20active%20on%20social%20media%20till%20yesterday%20however%2C%20their%20accounts%20were%20deleted%20after%20they%20were%20arrested.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20revelation%20that%20the%20alleged%20culprits%20were%20associated%20with%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20IT%20cell%20has%20also%20sparked%20a%20political%20controversy%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20The%20Samajwadi%20Party%E2%80%99s%20state%20spokesperson%2C%20Manoj%20Rai%20Dhupchandi%2C%20on%20Sunday%2C%20accused%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fvaranasi%2Fbjp-it-cell-duo-among-3-held-for-iit-bhu-girls-gang-rape%2Farticleshow%2F106426429.cms%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9Cwomen-worshipping%E2%80%9D%20saffron%20party%20of%20harbouring%20rapists.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20pictures%20of%20the%20accused%20with%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20top%20brass%20and%20other%20leaders%20have%20surfaced%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704094215000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F01113613%2FCopy-of-Lead-image-size-6.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwomen%2Fiit-bhu-gangrape-at-least-two-of-three-arrested-members-of-bjps-varanasi-it-cell%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Pictures%20of%20the%20accused%20with%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20top%20brass%20and%20other%20leaders%20have%20surfaced%20on%20social%20media.%22%2C%22au